20homes%20and%20residents%20say%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20find%20refuge%20or%20food%20in%20the%20densely%20populated%20coastal%20enclave.%20The%20U.N.%20World%20Food%20Programme%20has%20said%20half%20of%20the%20population%20is%20starving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHunger%20stalks%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20UNRWA%2C%20the%20U.N.%20body%20responsible%20for%20Palestinian%20refugees%2C%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGazans%20said%20people%20forced%20to%20flee%20repeatedly%20were%20dying%20of%20hunger%20and%20cold%20as%20well%20as%20the%20bombardments%2C%20describing%20looting%20of%20aid%20trucks%20and%20sky-high%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20says%20its%20instructions%20to%20people%20to%20move%20are%20among%20measures%20it%20is%20taking%20to%20protect%20civilians%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20root%20out%20Hamas%20militants%20who%20killed%201%2C200%20people%20and%20took%20240%20hostages%20in%20an%20Oct.%207%20cross-border%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20tallies.%20About%20100%20hostages%20have%20since%20been%20freed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20retaliatory%20assault%20has%20killed%2018%2C205%20people%20and%20wounded%20nearly%2050%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Gaza%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20193-member%20General%20Assembly%20is%20likely%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20pass%20a%20draft%20resolution%20that%20mirrors%20the%20language%20of%20one%20that%20was%20blocked%20by%20the%20United%20States%20in%20the%2015-member%20Security%20Council%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Assembly%20resolutions%20are%20not%20binding%20but%20carry%20political%20weight%20and%20reflect%20global%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20diplomats%20and%20observers%20predict%20the%20vote%20will%20garner%20greater%20support%20than%20the%20assembly's%20October%20call%20for%20%26quot%3Ban%20immediate%2C%20durable%20and%20sustained%20humanitarian%20truce.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScrutiny%20On%20US%20Support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vote%20was%20due%20a%20day%20after%2012%20Security%20Council%20envoys%20visited%20the%20Egyptian%20side%20of%20the%20Rafah%20border%20crossing%20with%20Gaza%2C%20the%20only%20place%20where%20limited%20humanitarian%20aid%20and%20fuel%20have%20entered.%20The%20United%20States%20did%20not%20send%20a%20representative%20on%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Department%20spokesperson%20Matthew%20Miller%20told%20reporters%20on%20Monday%20that%20Israel%20was%20no%20exception%20to%20U.S.%20policy%20that%20any%20country%20receiving%20its%20weapons%20must%20comply%20with%20the%20laws%20of%20war%20after%20Washington%20sold%20about%2014%2C000%20tank%20shells%20to%20Israel%20without%20congressional%20review%2C%20using%20an%20emergency%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20monitoring%20everything%20that%20happens%20in%20this%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20engaged%20in%20conversations%20with%20the%20Israeli%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20war%20has%20intensified%2C%20how%20and%20where%20Israel%20uses%20weapons%20from%20the%20U.S.%20has%20come%20under%20more%20scrutiny%2C%20even%20though%20U.S.%20officials%20say%20there%20are%20no%20plans%20to%20put%20conditions%20on%20military%20aid%20to%20Israel%20or%20to%20consider%20withholding%20some%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20found%20images%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20showing%20Palestinian%20men%20detained%20in%20Gaza%20in%20their%20underwear%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20disturbing%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20Israel%20to%20clarify%20the%20circumstances%20around%20the%20photographs%2C%20Miller%20added.%20Israel%20has%20said%20the%20men%20were%20stripped%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20were%20not%20hiding%20explosives%20or%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20also%20said%20on%20Monday%20it%20was%20concerned%20about%20reports%20Israel%20used%20U.S.-supplied%20white%20phosphorus%20munitions%20in%20an%20October%20attack%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%20and%20was%20seeking%20more%20information.%20The%20munitions%2C%20which%20can%20be%20legally%20used%20on%20battlefields%20to%20make%20smoke%20screens%20among%20other%20uses%2C%20can%20cause%20serious%20burns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20an%20allegation%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20that%20it%20uses%20white%20phosphorus%20munitions%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Lebanon%20was%20%26quot%3Bunequivocally%20false%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Aid%20Screening%20System%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.N.%20officials%20say%201.9%20million%20people%20-%2085%25%20of%20Gaza's%20population%20-%20are%20displaced%20and%20describe%20the%20conditions%20in%20the%20southern%20areas%20where%20they%20have%20concentrated%20as%20hellish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20increase%20the%20amount%20of%20aid%20reaching%20Gaza%2C%20Israel%20said%20on%20Monday%20it%20would%20add%20shipment%20screening%20at%20the%20Kerem%20Shalom%20border%20crossing%20even%20though%20it%20was%20not%20opening%20the%20crossing%20itself.%20Most%20trucks%20entered%20the%20strip%20at%20this%20crossing%20before%20the%20war.%20Two%20Egyptian%20security%20sources%20said%20inspections%20would%20begin%20on%20Tuesday%20under%20a%20new%20deal%20between%20Israel%2C%20Egypt%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20week-long%20ceasefire%20on%20Dec.%201%2C%20Israel%20began%20a%20ground%20offensive%20in%20the%20south%20and%20has%20since%20pushed%20from%20the%20east%20into%20the%20heart%20of%20Khan%20Younis%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20militants%20and%20residents%20said%20fighters%20were%20preventing%20Israeli%20tanks%20from%20moving%20farther%20west%20and%20clashing%20with%20Israeli%20forces%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20where%20Israel%20had%20said%20its%20mission%20was%20largely%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20dozens%20of%20Hamas%20fighters%20had%20surrendered%20and%20urged%20others%20to%20join%20them.%3C%2Fp%