-123121200070_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Another%20Ploy%20to%20Dupe%20Pandits'%3A%20Criticism%20Over%20Bills%20Aiming%20to%20'Reserve'%20Seats%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20Assembly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28124704%2FUntitled-design-3-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20section%20of%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20is%20not%20convinced%20by%20the%20claims%20being%20made%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-passed-two-important-laws-on-jk-heres-what-they-will-do%5C%22%3Elatest%20Bills%3C%2Fa%3E%20passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20concerning%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20would%20empower%20their%20community.%20They%20say%20the%20%E2%80%9Creservation%E2%80%9D%20being%20promised%20to%20Pandits%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20legislative%20assembly%20through%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20and%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Reservation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cploy%20to%20dupe%20people%20%5BPandits%5D%20into%20believing%20their%20%5BBJP%E2%80%99s%5D%20claims%20again%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Bills%20passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%206%20seek%20to%20nominate%20two%20members%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9CKashmiri%20migrant%20community%E2%80%9D%20and%20one%20representing%20the%20displaced%20persons%20from%20Pakistan%20Occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%20to%20the%20legislative%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Pandits%20say%20it%20is%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Creservation%E2%80%9D%20of%20seats%20per%20se%2C%20as%20the%20government%20is%20claiming%2C%20but%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnomination%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20political%20nature%2C%20which%20they%20say%2C%20would%20not%20empower%20the%20community%20politically%20in%20any%20way.%20Political%20analysts%20and%20activists%20from%20Kashmir%20also%20concur%20with%20the%20view%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20aimed%20at%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-passed-two-important-laws-on-jk-heres-what-they-will-do%5C%22%3E%20helping%20the%20BJP%20politically%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98A%20political%20move%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20been%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20nine%20years.%20While%20the%20BJP%2C%20in%20both%20its%20manifestos%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20spoke%20of%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%2C%20little%20has%20been%20done%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20of%20the%20community%2C%20say%20a%20section%20of%20community%20leaders.%20According%20to%20them%2C%20every%20move%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20supposedly%20aimed%20at%20their%20community%2C%20has%20added%20no%20value%20to%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatish%20Mahaldar%2C%20a%20community%20leader%2C%20says%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20Pandits%20have%20been%20more%20dejected%20than%20ever%20before.%20Mahaldar%20is%20the%20chairman%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Peace%20Forum%20as%20well%20as%20Reconciliation%2C%20Return%2C%20and%20Rehabilitation%20of%20Migrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20simply%20a%20political%20move%20aimed%20at%20helping%20the%20BJP.%20Had%20it%20been%20really%20concerned%20about%20the%20community%2C%20it%20would%20have%20reserved%20seats%20in%20a%20manner%20allowing%20people%20to%20elect%20their%20representatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20%E2%80%9Creservation%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20makes%20the%20voting%20rights%20of%20Pandits%20irrelevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F22202559%2FIMG_2821.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F22202559%2FIMG_2821.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F22202559%2FIMG_2821-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F22202559%2FIMG_2821-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-481030%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20protest%20by%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20in%20Srinagar.%20Photo%3A%20Shakir%20Mir%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%202014%20manifesto%2C%20the%20BJP%20vowed%20to%20facilitate%20the%20%E2%80%9Creturn%20of%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20to%20the%20land%20of%20their%20ancestors%20with%20full%20dignity%2C%20security%2C%20and%20assured%20livelihood%E2%80%9D.%20Similarly%2C%20in%20its%202019%20manifesto%2C%20it%20promised%20the%20%E2%80%9Csafe%20return%20of%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%E2%80%9D.%20But%20for%20Mahaldar%20and%20many%20other%20Pandits%2C%20the%20fulfilment%20of%20these%20promises%20by%20the%20BJP%20remains%20a%20pipedream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHave%20they%20been%20able%20to%20rehabilitate%20our%20community%2C%20even%20after%20their%20grand%20promises%3F%20No!%20This%20reservation%20is%20also%20a%20similar%20ploy%20to%20dupe%20people%20into%20believing%20their%20claims%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%20failed%20us%20on%20all%20promises.%20Why%20does%20the%20Bill%20mention%20%E2%80%98Kashmiri%20migrant%E2%80%99%20and%20not%20%E2%80%98Kashmiri%20Pandit%E2%80%99%3F%20What%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20Bill%20for%20us%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Mahaldar%20pointedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%20to%20add%20that%20he%2C%20along%20with%20his%20fellow%20Pandits%2C%20has%20been%20pitching%20development%20projects%20to%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%2C%20which%20he%20says%2C%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cignored%20and%20sidelined%E2%80%9D.%20The%20projects%20proposed%2C%20he%20says%2C%20were%20housing%20societies%20and%20schools%20for%20Pandits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20scheme%20of%20%E2%80%9Creservation%E2%80%9D%20will%20only%20continue%20to%20perpetuate%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinjustice%E2%80%9D%20being%20meted%20out%20to%20Pandits%2C%20says%20Bharat%20Kachroo%2C%20a%20social%20activist.%20Kachroo%20is%20from%20Jammu%E2%80%99s%20Jagti%20Camp%2C%20which%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20in%202011%20as%20a%20home%20for%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20migrants%20who%20fled%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20extremism%20and%20violence%20in%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20kind%20of%20reservation%20continues%20to%20deprive%20us%20constitutionally%2C%20democratically%2C%20and%20electorally%20because%20if%20we%20cannot%20vote%20for%20those%20who%20represent%20us%2C%20it%20is%20only%20a%20loss%20and%20injustice.%20These%20nominated%20leaders%20would%20be%20parachute%20leaders%2C%20working%20on%20commands%20of%20the%20LG%20and%20Union%20government.%20Had%20this%20been%20through%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20it%20would%20have%20made%20sense%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kachroo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20could%20have%20conducted%20elections%20within%20the%20community%20if%20they%20really%20wanted%20the%20Pandit%20community%20to%20have%20a%20voice.%20We%20would%20have%20respected%20that%2C%20but%20this%20only%20makes%20me%20think%20that%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20want%20to%20resettle%20us%20back%20into%20the%20Valley.%20This%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20our%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Nomination%2C%20not%20reservation%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Bill%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Reservation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbuttkout%5C%22%3EMohit%20Bhan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20from%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20it%20is%20not%20%E2%80%9Creservation%E2%80%9D%20but%20%E2%80%9Csimple%20nomination%20by%20the%20LG%E2%80%99s%20office%E2%80%9D.%20To%20call%20it%20reservation%2C%20he%20says%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmisconception%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20arrangement%20had%20already%20been%20in%20place%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%20state%20where%20representatives%20of%20various%20communities%20were%20nominated%20to%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20legislative%20council%2C%20which%20was%20also%20abolished%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhan%20affirms%20that%20nominations%20do%20not%20empower%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%2C%20for%20it%20does%20not%20help%20them%20in%20gaining%20political%20ground.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20he%20says%2C%20it%20has%20the%20reverse%20effect%20of%20pulling%20them%20back%20from%20grassroots%20political%20activity%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Tickoo%2C%20another%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20leader%2C%20concurs%20with%20Bhan.%20He%20feels%20that%20the%20nomination%20route%20would%20yield%20nothing%20and%20does%20not%20benefit%20the%20community.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20nominated%20people%20earlier%2C%20but%20it%20has%20made%20our%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tickoo%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20Sangharsh%20Samiti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETickoo%20alleges%20that%20there%20are%20no%20efforts%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20Union%20territory%20to%20help%20resettle%20the%20migrant%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20into%20the%20Valley.%20%E2%80%9CA%20sizeable%20number%20of%20community%20members%20had%20believed%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20resettle%20us%20back%20into%20the%20Valley%20and%20also%20give%20us%20rights.%20But%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20such%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Tickoo%2C%20who%20has%20stayed%20put%20in%20the%20Valley%20throughout%20despite%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20keep%20its%20promises%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20majority%20in%20the%20Valley%20turning%20against%20Pandits.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20only%20after%20the%20BJP%20government%20abrogated%20Article%20370%20that%20the%20first%20killing%20of%20a%20Pandit%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Valley%20after%2018%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Bhan%20and%20Tickoo%20say%20in%20unison%20that%20the%20Pandit%20community%20feels%20%E2%80%9Cbetrayed%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbackstabbed%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Bill%20set%20to%20become%20a%20law%20merely%20five%20months%20before%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20Bhan%20says%20the%20BJP%20only%20wants%20to%20milk%20the%20issues%20faced%20by%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20for%20its%20political%20gains.%20He%20says%20it%20only%20helps%20the%20BJP%20to%20advance%20its%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHindu%20khatrey%20main%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Hindus%20are%20under%20threat)%20%E2%80%9D%20narrative%20to%20woo%20Hindu%20voters%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702344505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28124704%2FUntitled-design-3-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanother-ploy-to-dupe-pandits-criticism-over-bills-aiming-to-reserve-seats-in-jk-assembly%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20community%20leaders%20say%20it%20is%20not%20a%20'reservation'%20of%20seats%20per%20se%2C%20as%20the%20government%20is%20claiming%2C%20but%20a%20'nomination'%20of%20a%20political%20nature%2C%20which%20they%20say%2C%20would%20not%20empower%20the%20community%20politically%20in%20any%20way.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanother-ploy-to-dupe-pandits-criticism-over-bills-aiming-to-reserve-seats-in-jk-assembly%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22David%