%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20men%2C%20including%20two%20shooters%2C%20arrested%20for%20their%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20case%20were%20produced%20before%20a%20local%20court%20and%20remanded%20to%20police%20custody%20for%20seven%20days%20by%20the%20magistrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20apprehended%20the%20shooters%20--%20Nitin%20Fauji%20and%20Rohit%20Rathore%20--%20along%20with%20their%20accomplice%20Udham%20Singh%20from%20sector%2022%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Saturday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaipur%20Police%20Commissioner%20Biju%20George%20Joseph%20said%20Pooja%20Saini%20and%20her%20husband%20Mahendra%20Meghwal%20provided%20weapons%20to%20Fauji%20who%20stayed%20in%20the%20couple's%20rented%20flat%20in%20the%20Jagatpura%20area%20of%20Jaipur%20for%20nearly%20a%20week%20before%20carrying%20out%20the%20killing%20on%20December%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeghwal%20alias%20Sameer%20is%20from%20Kota%20and%20is%20on%20run%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20Kailash%20Chandra%20Bishnoi%20said%20Fauji%20came%20to%20Jaipur%20in%20a%20taxi%20on%20November%2028%20and%20met%20Meghwal%20who%20took%20him%20to%20the%20flat%20in%20Jagatpura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20through%20Meghwal%20that%20Fauji%20remained%20in%20touch%20with%20gangster%20Rohit%20Godara%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodara%2C%20linked%20to%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20had%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20Gogamedi's%20killing%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20saying%20the%20Karni%20Sena%20chief%20was%20backing%20his%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20Meghwal%20had%20procured%20more%20than%20half%20a%20dozen%20pistols%20and%20cartridges%20in%20large%20quantities.%20Fauji%20took%20two%20pistols%20and%20as%20many%20magazines%20for%20him%20and%20one%20pistol%20and%20two%20magazines%20for%20Rathore%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPooja%20also%20prepared%20food%20for%20Fauji%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20December%205%2C%20Meghwal%20dropped%20Fauji%20on%20Ajmer%20Road%20where%20Rathore%20was%20waiting%20for%20him.%20The%20armed%20duo%20was%20then%20taken%20to%20the%20residence%20of%20Gogamedi%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Shri%20Rashtriya%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%2C%20in%20Jaipur's%20Shyam%20Nagar%20area%20in%20a%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20secured%20access%20to%20Gogamedi's%20house%20through%20Naveen%20Shekhawat%20who%20was%20acquainted%20with%20the%20Karni%20Sena%20chief.%20After%20talking%20to%20him%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20the%20shooters%20opened%20fire%20at%20Gogamedi%20in%20his%20living%20room%2C%20leaving%20him%20dead.%20They%20also%20killed%20Shekhawat%20before%20fleeing%20from%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBishnoi%20said%20a%20photo%20of%20an%20AK-47%20rifle%20was%20also%20recovered%20from%20Meghwal's%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubstantial%20evidence%20has%20been%20recovered%20from%20the%20flat%20which%20indicates%20that%20a%20network%20of%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20was%20operating%20from%20there.%20During%20the%20investigation%2C%20it%20came%20to%20light%20that%20the%20couple%20had%20provided%20weapons%20for%20the%20crime%20executed%20by%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20in%20Jaipur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20operation%20conducted%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20Police%20and%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20Fauji%2C%20Rathore%20and%20Singh%20were%20arrested%20from%20outside%20a%20Chandigarh%20hotel%20and%20brought%20to%20Jaipur%20amid%20tight%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFauji%2C%20hailing%20from%20Haryana's%20Mahendragarh%2C%20is%20a%20lance%20naik%20in%20the%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702342260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffet4lmeo_sukh