%20non-Apple%20users%20from%20accessing%20iMessage%20as%20a%20way%20to%20protect%20%26quot%3Bsecurity%20and%20privacy.%26quot%3B%20It%20also%20said%20that%20it%20would%20continue%20to%20make%20updates%20to%20protect%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeeper%20said%20that%20it%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20share%20its%20entire%20codebase%20with%20Apple%20if%20security%20was%20a%20concern%20in%20its%20blog%20post.%20It%20also%20called%20Apple's%20statement%20%26quot%3B1984-esque.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeeper%20allows%20for%20perks%20like%20high-quality%20images%2C%20emojis%2C%20read%20receipts%2C%20and%20type%20status%20to%20be%20used%20in%20cross-platform%20messaging.%20It%20also%20gave%20Android%20users%20the%20blue%20text%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeeper%20co-founder%20Eric%20Migocvsky%20previously%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimessage-android-app-beeper-mini-blue-bubble-texts-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20allowing%20non-iPhone%20users%20access%20to%20iMessage%20was%20something%20that%20benefitted%20both%20iPhone%20and%20Android%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20move%20to%20block%20Beeper%20Mini%20was%20also%20criticized%20by%20Sen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EGreen%20bubble%20texts%20are%20less%20secure.%20So%20why%20would%20Apple%20block%20a%20new%20app%20allowing%20Android%20users%20to%20chat%20with%20iPhone%20users%20on%20iMessage%3F%20Big%20Tech%20executives%20are%20protecting%20profits%20by%20squashing%20competitors.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EChatting%20between%20different%20platforms%20should%20be%20easy%20and%20secure.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FfHAS5ckaEA%5C%22