y%20on%20the%20drugs%20long-term%20to%20maintain%20it.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Dazeley%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETirzepatide%2C%20a%20drug%20newly%20approved%20to%20treat%20obesity%2C%20helped%20people%20lose%2020%25%20of%20body%20weight%20on%20average.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20growing%20evidence%20suggests%20patients%20need%20to%20keep%20taking%20the%20drug%20to%20maintain%20the%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPeople%20who%20stopped%20taking%20the%20drug%20regained%20more%20than%20half%20what%20they%20lost%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20even%20more%20evidence%20that%20a%20wildly%20popular%20medication%20can%20help%20people%20lose%20significant%20weight%20and%20keep%20it%20off%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20if%20they%20continue%20taking%20the%20drug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftirzepatide-weight-loss-drug-vs-semaglutide-glp-1-agonist-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETirzepatide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20once-weekly%20injection%2C%20is%20part%20of%20a%20group%20of%20medications%20that%20work%20by%20acting%20on%20a%20hormone%20called%20GLP-1%20to%20help%20regulate%20appetite%20and%20blood%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20has%20been%20available%20for%20diabetes%20treatment%20since%202022%2C%20sold%20under%20the%20brand%20name%20Mounjaro%2C%20.%20It%20was%20FDA-approved%20specifically%20for%20weight%20management%20in%20November%20of%20this%20year%20under%20the%20brand%20name%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Feli-lilly-mounjaro-zepbound-approved-weight-loss-stronger-than-wegovy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZepbound%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20taking%20tirzepatide%20lost%20an%20average%20of%20nearly%2050%20pounds%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%2C%20but%20gained%20more%20than%20half%20of%20it%20back%20if%20they%20stopped%20taking%20the%20drug%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20published%20December%2011%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjama%2Ffullarticle%2F2812936%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJAMA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20researchers%20from%20several%20universities%2C%20including%20Weill%20Cornell%20Medicine%2C%20looked%20at%20670%20people%20on%20tirzepatide%20as%20part%20of%20a%20clinical%20trial%20funded%20by%20the%20drug's%20manufacturer%2C%20pharmaceutical%20company%20Eli%20Lilly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20participants%20took%20tirzepatide%20for%2036%20weeks%2C%20during%20which%20they%20lost%20an%20average%20of%2020%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%20(roughly%2046%20pounds).%20Then%2C%20one%20group%20of%20patients%20was%20randomly%20assigned%20to%20a%20placebo%20instead%20of%20continuing%20the%20medication%20for%20the%20next%2052%20weeks.%20The%20patients%20in%20the%20other%20group%20were%20assigned%20to%20continue%20taking%20the%20drug%20during%20this%20time%20(although%20not%20all%20of%20the%20patients%20in%20either%20group%20completed%20the%20study%2C%20often%20for%20reasons%20unrelated%20to%20the%20medication).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20found%20that%20people%20who%20stopped%20taking%20tirzepatide%20regained%20about%2014%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20half%20of%20what%20they%20had%20initially%20lost%20%E2%80%94%20over%20the%20year%20of%20follow-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20group%20who%20kept%20taking%20the%20drug%20not%20only%20maintained%20their%20results%2C%20but%20went%20on%20to%20lose%20even%20more%20weight%20(an%20additional%205.5%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%2C%20on%20average)%20over%2052%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20placebo%20group%20still%20ended%20up%20lighter%20than%20they%20had%20been%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20study%2C%20the%20results%20add%20to%20existing%20evidence%20that%20tirzepatide%20and%20similar%20drugs%20only%20work%20as%20long%20as%20patients%20keep%20taking%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESemaglutide%2C%20sold%20as%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%2C%20works%20the%20same%20way%2C%20as%20patients%20who%20stopped%20taking%20the%20drug%20regained%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20weight%20they%20had%20lost%2C%20according%20to%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F35441470%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20also%20underscore%20what%20doctors%20have%20previously%20known%20about%20these%20medications%3A%20patients%20need%20to%20take%20them%20long-term%2C%20and%20possibly%20for%20life%2C%20to%20maintain%20the%20health%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20phenomenon%20isn't%20unique%20to%20drugs%20used%20for%20weight%20management.%20Many%20common%20medications%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20continuously%20in%20order%20to%20help%20treat%20chronic%20conditions%20such%20as%20hypertension%2C%20diabetes%2C%20or%20high%20cholesterol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20doctors%20have%20previously%20said%20that%20patients%20can%20face%20major%20obstacles%20if%20staying%20on%20the%20medications%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESides%20effects%2C%20shortages%2C%20and%20a%20high%20price%20tag%20can%20make%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20difficult%20to%20take%20long-term%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20research%20suggests%20that%20as%20many%20as%20two-thirds%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmost-patients-stop-weight-loss-drugs-wegovy-after-one-year-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20on%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20stop%20taking%20them%20within%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFactors%20like%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20drugs%2C%20ability%20to%20get%20them%2C%20and%20unwanted%20effects%20can%20all%20play%20role%20in%20people%20opting%20to%20discontinue%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20tirzepatide%20is%20considered%20safe%2C%20it%20does%20have%20well-documented%20side%20effects%2C%20typically%20mild%20to%20moderate%20gastrointestinal%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20most%20recent%20study%2C%2080%25%20of%20patients%20reported%20at%20least%20one%20side%20effect%2C%20usually%20nausea%2C%20diarrhea%2C%20constipation%2C%20or%20vomiting.%20And%20six%20people%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20tirzepatide%20group%20in%20the%20follow-up%20year%20due%20to%20side%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmounjaro-vs-ozempic-side-effects-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESymptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20usually%20resolve%20over%20time%2C%20and%20gradually%20working%20up%20to%20the%20correct%20dose%20can%20help%2C%20too%2C%20doctors%20previously%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20another%20concern%20for%20doctors%20is%20that%20patients%20sometimes%20struggle%20to%20afford%20the%20medications%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmounjaro-cost-without-coupon-regain-weight-loss-drug-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20cost%20%241%2C000%20or%20more%20per%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20may%20not%20be%20covered%20by%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fnew-weight-loss-drugs-popularity-evidence-and-side-effects-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20demand%20for%20the%20medications%20has%20also%20prompted%20shortages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20to%20limited%20availability%20for%20patients%20who%20need%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20even%20people%20who%20have%20seen%20%26quot%3Blife%20changing%26quot%3B%20results%20may%20struggle%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20medications%20if%20they%20can't%20afford%20them%2C%20or%20even%20fill%20their%20prescriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzepbound-weight-gain-stop-taking-tirzepatide-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702336527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6577658d58e7c0c29a2bc5bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originI