0to%20Miami%20on%20November%2030.%20During%20a%20short%20layover%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Schreib%20used%20the%20restroom%2C%20where%20she%20first%20spotted%20unruly%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20of%20them%20were%20walking%20arm%20and%20arm%2C%20stumbling%20drunk%2C%20and%20ran%20right%20into%20me%20in%20the%20bathroom%2C%26quot%3B%20Schreib%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20crazy%20because%20it%20was%207%3A30%20in%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20Schreib%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20expect%20that%20at%20that%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchreib%20boarded%20her%20flight%20with%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20women%20from%20the%20restroom%20took%20a%20seat%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20She%20watched%20the%20woman%20start%20conversing%20with%20the%20men%20in%20her%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20slurring%20her%20words%20and%20can%20barely%20talk%2C%26quot%3B%20Schreib%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20woman%20should%20not%20be%20on%20this%20plane.%20I%20was%20concerned%2C%20honestly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20took%20off%2C%20Schreib%20said.%20Later%2C%20she%20said%20she%20noticed%20that%20the%20two%20men%20seated%20with%20the%20intoxicated%20passenger%20relocated%20to%20other%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20I%20became%20aware%20of%20a%20vile%20smell.%20I%20thought%2C%20'Oh%20god%20she%20must%20be%20getting%20sick%2C'%26quot%3B%20Schreib%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight%20attendants%20came%20over%20and%20offered%20the%20passenger%20ginger%20ale%20and%20water.%20Schreib%20said%20she%20assumed%20the%20woman%20was%20using%20an%20airplane%20vomit%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20plane%20neared%20landing%2C%20Schreib%20grabbed%20her%20canvas%20tote%20that%20was%20stored%20underneath%20the%20seat%20in%20front%20of%20her%20and%20discovered%20it%20was%20covered%20in%20vomit.%20So%20was%20her%20purse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20believe%20the%20amount%2C%26quot%3B%20Schreib%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20was%20unable%20to%20verify%20the%20claims%20of%20vomit%2C%20as%20Schreib%20did%20not%20take%20photos%20in%20her%20haste%20to%20clean%20it%20up%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20questioned%20why%20no%20one%20had%20cleaned%20up%20the%20vomit%20earlier%2C%20she%20said%20a%20flight%20attendant%20told%20her%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bcan't%20do%20anything%20about%20that.%20It's%20bodily%20fluids%2C%20and%20we%20can't%20touch%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20publication%2C%20BI%20was%20unable%20to%20confirm%20this%20policy%20with%20American%20Airlines%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20it%20on%20their%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchreib%20said%20she%20disembarked%20the%20flight%20frustrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20kind%20of%20freak%20out%20a%20little%20bit%20when%20someone%20else's%20vomit%20is%20on%20your%20belongings%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Images%20of%20a%20passenger%20with%20their%20legs%20up%20on%20the%20wall%20of%20an%20aircraft.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657346120ec98e92f74d8987%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EImages%20of%20a%20passenger%20with%20their%20legs%20up%20on%20the%20wall%20of%20an%20aircraft.%3Cp%3ENicole%20Schreib%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ESchreib%20reached%20out%20to%20American%20Airlines%20in%20search%20of%20an%20apology%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20Schreib%20emailed%20American%20Airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20an%20hour%2C%20I%20had%20a%20response%20from%20American%20Airlines%2C%20which%20was%20surprising%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20was%20even%20more%20surprising%20was%20that%20they%20took%20absolutely%20no%20responsibility%20for%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20an%20American%20Airlines%20representative%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20sorry%20to%20hear%20your%20property%20was%20damaged%20by%20another%20passenger.%20While%20I%20can%20certainly%20understand%20your%20frustration%20with%20the%20situation%2C%20unintentional%20things%20can%20and%20do%20happen%20in%20public%20spaces.%20Although%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20you%20were%20involved%20in%20this%20situation%2C%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20actions%20of%20another%20individual.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchreib%20pushed%20back%20and%20ultimately%20received%20a%20%2450%20voucher.%20Still%20frustrated%2C%20Schreib%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20responded%20to%20Schreib%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bsorry%20to%20hear%20you%20weren't%20satisfied%20by%20the%20resolution%20of%20your%20claim.%20You%20can%20request%20a%20review%20by%20replying%20to%20the%20last%20email%20they%20sent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20last%20she%20heard%20from%20the%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20about%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20about%20taking%20a%20little%20responsibility%20and%20actually%20apologizing%20for%20what%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere%20aren't%20set%20standards%20for%20how%20passengers%20are%20compensated%20in%20situations%20like%20this.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchreib%20isn't%20the%20first%20airline%20passenger%20to%20encounter%20another%20traveler's%20vomit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fair-canada-passengers-kicked-off-plane-refused-puke-covered-seats-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20two%20Air%20Canada%20passengers%20were%20asked%20to%20leave%20a%20plane%20after%20they%20refused%20to%20sit%20in%20seats%20with%20vomit%20residue%20from%20a%20passenger%20on%20the%20prior%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20airlines%20have%20formal%20policies%20to%20respond%20to%20flight%20delays%20or%20cancelations%2C%20there%20are%20no%20comparable%20standards%20for%20this%20type%20of%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaty%20Nastro%2C%20a%20travel%20expert%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgoing.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoing.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20fly%20with%20an%20airline%2C%20you%20are%20agreeing%20to%20their%20contract%20of%20carriage%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20an%20agreement%20between%20you%20and%20the%20airlines%20based%20on%20the%20fact%20you%20bought%20a%20ticket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20contract%20might%20cover%20things%20like%20showing%20valid%20ID%2C%20dressing%20appropriately%2C%20and%20behaving%20respectfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20should%20be%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20airline%20to%20deal%20with%20this%20erratic%20passenger%20upon%20boarding%2C%20but%20it%20isn't%20clear%20whether%20the%20cleanliness%20factor%20is%20guaranteed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20basic%20level%20of%20cleanliness%20sure%2C%20but%20if%20another%20passenger%20spills%20a%20drink%2C%20or%20in%20this%20instance%20gets%20sick%20and%20it%20invades%20the%20space%20of%20the%20other%20passengers%2C%20to%20my%20knowledge%20there%20is%20no%20item%20in%20American%20Airline's%20contract%20of%20carriage%20that%20promises%20anything%20in%20return.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20Schreib%20said%20she's%20going%20to%20think%20twice%20before%20booking%20another%20American%20Airlines%20flight.%20And%20for%20all%20future%20flights%2C%20she%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bcertainly%20will%20be%20bringing%20a%20bag%20that%20is%20waterproof.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-passenger-says-woman-vomited-bags-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702326822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.in