how%2F105913066.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fossil%20fuel%20backlash%20puts%20UN%20climate%20talks%20in%20jeopardy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702322166000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F89C3%2Fproduction%2F_131976253_gettyimages-1836049142.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67679732%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20summit%20had%20appeared%20close%20to%20calling%20for%20a%20phase-out%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20but%20made%20last-minute%20changes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A296%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67679732%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67679732.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67679732.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahead%20Of%20Ram%20Temple%20Opening%20In%20Ayodhya%2C%20An%20Infra%2C%20Real%20Estate%20Boom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20inauguration%20of%20the%20long-awaited%20Ram%20Mandir%20only%20weeks%20away%2C%20the%20once-sleepy%20town%20of%20Ayodhya%20is%20going%20through%20an%20infrastructure%20overhaul.%20This%20has%20caused%20a%20real%20estate%20boom%20in%20the%20city%20with%20property%20prices%20sky%20rocketing.%20Investors%2C%20hoteliers%20and%20business%20owners%20have%20rushed%20into%20the%20city%2C%20pushing%20up%20property%20prices%20by%20as%20much%20as%20thrice%20the%20original%20price%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnLocal%20property%20dealers%20say%20there%20are%20hardly%20any%20properties%20are%20left%20to%20buy.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20now%20land%20available%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20property%20dealer%20Kakku%20Singh.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BIn%20the%20outer%20areas%2C%20where%20the%20rates%20should%20have%20been%20around%20Rs%203%2C000...%20The%20rates%20have%20gone%20up%20to%20Rs%206%2C000%20to%20Rs%207%2C000...%20Around%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20there%20is%20no%20land...%20if%20there%20is%2C%20here%20is%20no%20rate...%20A%20person%20can%20get%20whatever%20they%20ask%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnData%20from%20Ayodhya's%20Stamp%20and%20Registration%20Department%20shows%20in%202018-19%2C%20around%209%2C000%20properties%20were%20sold%20till%20November.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20corresponding%20figure%20has%20more%20than%20doubled.%20Till%20November%2C%2020%2C067%20properties%20have%20been%20sold%20this%20year%2C%20data%20shows.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20prices%20have%20been%20peaking%20as%20the%20date%20of%20inauguration%20approaches.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revenue%20generated%20by%20the%20department%20has%20risen%20to%20Rs%2015%2C631.33%20lakh%20up%20till%20November%20this%20year%20from%20around%2010%2C000%20lakh%20in%202018-19.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Department's%20revenue%20receipt%20for%20November%20in%20terms%20of%20per%20cent%20hike%20was%20109%20per%20cent%20--%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20receive%20phone%20calls%20from%20people%20who%20want%20to%20buy%20land%20to%20start%20hotels%2C%20resorts...%20So%20this%20has%20increased%20the%20revenue%20of%20the%20Stamp%20Department%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yogendra%20Pratap%2C%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20Stamp%20%26amp%3B%20Registration%20Department.%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20locals%20hope%20the%20investment%20will%20bring%20tourists%20and%20provide%20a%20means%20of%20income%20for%20many.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajjan%20Lal%2C%20who%20lives%2040%20km%20from%20Ayodhya%2C%20has%20sold%20of%20his%20property%20in%20the%20village%20and%20bought%20a%201000%20sq%20ft%20plot%20to%20start%20a%20small%20shop%20selling%20cement%20near%20Ayodhya%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20booming%20infrastructure%20expansion.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20the%20temple%20construction%2C%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20to%20have%20good%20income...I%20will%20do%20business%20here%2C%20but%20the%20rates%20are%20high%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20government%20is%20also%20planning%20to%20build%20a%204.40-acre%20Tourism%20Facilitation%20Center%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20estimated%20cost%20will%20be%20Rs%20130-%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20project%2C%20various%20commercial%20centres%2C%20including%20a%20tourism%20office%2C%20passenger%20accommodation%2C%20art%20and%20craft%20centre%2C%20food%20court%2C%20shopping%20mart%2C%20and%20parking%20space%2C%20will%20be%20developed%20in%20the%20tourist%20centre.%20The%20project%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20off%20shortly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20airport%20being%20built%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20finished%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month%2C%20Union%20aviation%20minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702321980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fl2ckttlg_ayodhya-airport_625x300_11_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-ram-temple-opening-in-ayodhya-an-infra-real-estate-boom-4656221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20inauguration%20of%20the%20long-awaited%20Ram%20Mandir%20only%20weeks%20away%2C%20the%20once-sleepy%20town%20of%20Ayodhya%20is%20going%20through%20an%20infrastructure%20overhaul.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-ram-temple-opening-in-ayodhya-an-infra-real-estate-boom-4656221%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-ram-temple-opening-in-ayodhya-an-infra-real-estate-boom-4656221%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F