passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20Delimitation%20Commission%2C%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20delimitation%20of%20assemblies%20and%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20has%20reserved%2024%20seats%20for%20PoK%20as%20it%20is%20ours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20delimitation%20commission%20has%20taken%20many%20other%20decisions.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20past%20and%20present%20situation%20before%20the%20House.%20Earlier%20there%20were%20only%2037%20seats%20in%20Jammu%20(division)%2C%20now%20the%20new%20Delimitation%20Commission%20has%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20from%2037%20to%2043%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region.%20Work%20has%20been%20done%20to%20make%2047%20seats%20instead%20of%2046%20in%20Kashmir%20(division).%20In%20this%20way%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20together%20have%2090%20seats%20against%2083%20seats%20earlier.%20And%2024%20seats%20of%20PoK%20have%20been%20kept%20reserved%20because%20we%20still%20believe%20that...(and)%20today%20I%20want%20to%20say%20again%20that%20PoK%20belongs%20to%20India%2C%20it%20is%20ours%20and%20that%20no%20one%20can%20take%20it%20from%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reservation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20was%20introduced%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20July%2026%2C%202023.%20It%20amends%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reservation%20Act%20of%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Act%20provides%20for%20reservation%20in%20jobs%20and%20admission%20in%20professional%20institutions%20to%20members%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20and%20other%20socially%20and%20educationally%20backward%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20seeks%20to%20insert%20new%20sections%2015A%20and%2015B%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019%20to%20nominate%20not%20more%20than%20two%20members%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20shall%20be%20a%20woman%2C%20from%20the%20community%20of%20%26quot%3BKashmiri%20Migrants%26quot%3B%20and%20one%20member%20from%20%26quot%3BDisplaced%20Persons%20from%20Pakistan%20occupied%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20bills%20on%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reservation%20are%20aimed%20at%20providing%20%26quot%3Brights%20to%20those%20who%20faced%20injustice%26quot%3B%20and%20were%20deprived%20of%20their%20rights%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20that%20everyone%20has%20supported%20all%20the%20elements%20of%20the%20two%20bills%20unanimously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20term%20'weak%20and%20deprived%20class'%20is%20a%20very%20hurtful%20name%20for%20any%20citizen%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20add%20the%20name%20'Other%20Backward%20Class'%20in%20place%20of%20these%20terms%2C%20which%20are%20constitutional%20terms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20bill%20is%20to%20give%20respect%20to%20everyone%20including%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20displaced%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20over%20the%20years%2C%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTerrorism%20(in%20J-K)%20started%20in%20the%2080s%2C%20and%20reached%20its%20peak%20in%201989%2C%20many%20Kashmiri%20Hindus%2C%20especially%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20and%20many%20Sikh%20brothers%20left%20the%20valley%20and%20scattered%20across%20the%20country.%20They%20went%20to%20Jammu%2C%20went%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20went%20to%20Gujarat%2C%20went%20to%20Delhi%2C%20went%20to%20Faridabad...they%20scattered%20so%20much%20that%20in%20their%20own%20country%20they%20became%20displaced%20and%20refugees.%20(This%20bill)%20is%20to%20honour%20those%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20address%2C%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20said%20a%20total%20of%2046%2C631%20families%20and%201%2C97%2C967%20people%2C%20who%20were%20displaced%20registered%20themselves%20with%20the%20government%20after%20the%20Centre's%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20ones%20displaced%20including%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20who%20are%20left%20from%20registering%20themselves%20can%20approach%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20through%20this%20House%2C%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20and%20other%20displaced%20persons%20scattered%20across%20the%20country%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20providing%20you%20justice.%20You%20write%20to%20me%2C%20write%20to%20the%20Kashmir%20government.%20Your%20registration%20will%20be%20done%20without%20any%20hassle.%20You%20will%20become%20a%20voter%2C%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20contest%20elections%20and%20you%20can%20also%20become%20a%20minister%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20You%20have%20full%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702317000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fulj7roj8_amit-shah-_120x90_11_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpakistan-occupied-kashmir-is-ours-amit-shah-reiterates-in-rajya-sabha-4655779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Monday%20reaffirmed%20inside%20Parliament%20that%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%20is%20part%20of%20India%20and%20that%20no%20one%20can%20snatch%20the%20region%20from%20us.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpakistan-occupied-kashmir-is-ours-amit-shah-reiterates-in-rajya-sabha-4655779%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpakistan-occupied-k