%20a%20Dalit%20leader%20being%20chosen%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20will%20be%20revealed%20tomorrow.%E2%80%9D%20Former%20chief%20minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20and%20Union%20ministers%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%2C%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20and%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20are%20said%20to%20be%20in%20the%20running%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20one%20of%20three%20states%20that%20the%20BJP%20won%20in%20the%20recent%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLAs%20were%20informed%20Monday%20about%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20legislature%20party%2C%20where%20the%20BJP's%20central%20leadership%20will%20make%20known%20its%20choice%20for%20the%20post%2C%20nine%20days%20after%20the%20results%20of%20the%20November%2025%20elections%20came%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20115%20seats%20out%20of%20the%20199%20where%20polling%20took%20place.%20Polling%20was%20postponed%20in%20one%20constituency%20due%20to%20the%20death%20of%20a%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20Jogeshwar%20Garg%20said%20the%20observers%20will%20hold%20one-on-one%20talks%20with%20the%20MLAs%20before%20the%20meeting%20to%20formally%20elect%20the%20legislature%20party%20leader%2C%20or%20the%20CM-designate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20new%20legislators%20who%20met%20former%20chief%20minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20at%20her%20home%20Monday%2C%20Kirodi%20Lal%20Meena%20said%2017%20MLAs%20visited%20him%20as%20well%20after%20the%20results%20and%20this%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20lobbying.%20Meena%20resigned%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20after%20his%20election%20as%20an%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20MLAs%20have%20called%20on%20former%20Raje%20in%20recent%20days%20in%20what%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20show%20of%20support%2C%20amid%20speculation%20over%20what%20the%20party%20will%20decide.%20She%20also%20met%20party%20leaders%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajendra%20Rathore%2C%20who%20lost%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20have%20the%20show-of-strength%20culture.%20Neither%20does%20anybody%20has%20the%20courage%20to%20do%20so%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20MLAs%20go%20to%20meet%20senior%20leaders%20to%20exchange%20wishes%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20and%20asserted%20that%20all%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20the%20state%20are%20united.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rathore%20said%20the%20new%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20engine%E2%80%9D%20will%20take%20shape%20in%20Rajasthan%20tomorrow%2C%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20party%20holding%20power%20both%20in%20the%20state%20and%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702315140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fpi7i3n9k_rajasthan-vidhan-sabha-building-ani_625x300_11_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-suspense-ending-soon-bjp-meet-to-pick-chief-minister-tomorrow-4654572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20newly%20elected%20BJP%20MLAs%20in%20Rajasthan%20will%20meet%20in%20Jaipur%20Tuesday%20to%20formally%20pick%20the%20next%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%2C%20ending%20days%20of%20suspense%20after%20the%20party%20won%20the%20assembly%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-suspense-ending-soon-bjp-meet-to-pick-chief-minister-tomorrow-4654572%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-suspense-ending-soon-bjp-meet-to-pick-chief-minister-tomorrow-4654572%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-suspense-ending-soon-bjp-meet-to-pick-c