%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20legislature%20party%20finally%20elected%20the%2058-year-old%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20who%20held%20the%20higher%20education%20department%20as%20a%20minister%20under%20the%20outgoing%20BJP%20government%2C%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20choice%20to%20lead%20the%20central%20Indian%20state%2C%20in%20a%20move%20that%20caught%20most%20observers%20by%20surprise.%20While%20there%20were%20many%20BJP%20leaders%20said%20to%20be%20in%20the%20running%20for%20the%20CM%E2%80%99s%20post%20ever%20since%20the%20party%20won%20a%20thumping%20two-thirds%20majority%20on%20December%203%2C%20Yadav%20was%20not%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20would%20have%20two%20deputies%20%E2%80%93%20Jagdish%20Devda%20and%20Rajendra%20Shukla%20%E2%80%93%20both%20of%20whom%20have%20a%20long%20association%20with%20the%20party%20and%20have%20won%20multiple%20elections.%20Devda%20is%20a%20Dalit%2C%20while%20Shukla%20belongs%20to%20the%20Brahmin%20community.%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20who%20was%20parachuted%20back%20from%20Delhi%20to%20contest%20the%20Assembly%20election%2C%20will%20be%20the%20Speaker%20of%20the%20MP%20Assembly.%20For%20many%2C%20he%20had%20also%20been%20a%20serious%20contender%20for%20the%20CM%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20picking%20an%20OBC%2C%20a%20Dalit%2C%20and%20an%20%E2%80%98upper%20caste%E2%80%99%20to%20lead%20the%20state%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20has%20again%20demonstrated%20its%20tactic%20of%20balancing%20caste%20aspirations%20under%20a%20united%20Hindu%20political%20consciousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0The%20selection%20of%20Yadav%20as%20its%20CM%20in%20MP%20has%20also%20indicated%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20new%20leadership%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20it%20already%20has%20strong%20ideological%20and%20organisational%20roots%2C%20and%20cement%20its%20goodwill%20among%20the%20numerically-significant%20backward%20caste%20voters.%20Given%20that%20Yadav%20has%20no%20mass%20following%20of%20his%20own%20or%20proven%20record%20of%20charisma%2C%20the%20double-engine%20government%20appears%20to%20be%20lopsided%20with%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Centre%20assuming%20even%20more%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStructurally%2C%20the%20shift%20from%20Chouhan%20to%20Yadav%20is%20not%20that%20stark%20as%20both%20had%20a%20similar%20political%20trajectory%2C%20groomed%20in%20politics%20by%20the%20RSS%20and%20honing%20their%20skills%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Barring%20a%2015-month%20stint%20by%20Congress%20in%202018-2020%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20ruled%20MP%20since%202003%20without%20interruption.%20Much%20of%20that%20was%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20whose%20time%20as%20a%20CM%20also%20came%20to%20an%20end%2C%20for%20now%2C%20with%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20elevation.%20The%20party%20is%20yet%20to%20clear%20the%20air%20about%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20future%3A%20will%20he%20continue%20to%20play%20a%20dominant%20role%20in%20state%20politics%20as%20a%20powerful%20minister%20or%20will%20he%20take%20up%20a%20new%20role%20in%20national%20politics%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20and%20Chouhan%20exchanged%20the%20baton%20after%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20legislature%20meeting%20by%20putting%20up%20a%20show%20of%20unity.%20When%20Chouhan%20offered%20Yadav%20a%20bouquet%20to%20congratulate%20him%2C%20the%20latter%20responded%20by%20touching%20the%20outgoing%20CM%E2%80%99s%20feet%2C%20a%20gesture%20of%20respect.%20Chouhan%20then%20extended%20his%20hand%20and%20placed%20it%20over%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20head%20to%20bless%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYadav%3A%20An%20aggressive%20and%20shriller%20proponent%20of%20BJP%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Yadav%20won%20his%20third%20consecutive%20election%20from%20the%20Ujjain%20South%20seat%2C%20although%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20over%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20this%20time%20was%20thin%20(12%2C941%20votes).%20In%20Yadav%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20found%20an%20aggressive%20and%20shriller%20proponent%20of%20its%20politics%2C%20one%20who%20has%20risen%20in%20the%20organisational%20ladder%20of%20the%20party%20over%20the%20years%20and%20ultimately%20tasted%20electoral%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirija%20Shankar%2C%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20said%20by%20picking%20Yadav%20as%20CM%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20started%20building%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20generation%20of%20leaders%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20started.%20But%20how%20effective%20that%20will%20be%2C%20the%20coming%20times%20will%20tell%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharma%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20ever%20expected%20Yadav%20to%20become%20CM%2C%20Sharma%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20someone%20is%20elected%20as%20CM%2C%20at%20that%20time%20we%20cannot%20comment%20if%20he%20or%20she%20is%20worthy%20of%20the%20post.%20A%20person%20becomes%20a%20big%20leader%20after%20he%20or%20she%20gets%20an%20opportunity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20that%20accord%2C%20Yadav%2C%20though%20not%20that%20well-known%20outside%20MP%2C%20has%20immense%20experience%20as%20an%20organisation%20man%20and%20legislator.%20He%20started%20his%20political%20career%20in%20the%20early%201980s%20as%20a%20student%20leader.%20From%201986%20to%201997%20he%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20in%20his%20hometown%20Ujjain%20before%20working%20with%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20BJP%20of%20which%20he%20was%20appointed%20a%20state%20executive%20member%20in%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20held%20the%20post%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Ujjain%20general%20secretary%20from%202000%20to%202003%2C%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20state%20working%20committee%20in%202004%20and%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20executive.%20Yadav%20held%20the%20post%20of%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Ujjain%20Development%20Authority%20from%202004%20to%202010%20and%20the%20president%20of%20the%20MP%20State%20Tourism%20Development%20Corporation%20from%202011%20to%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20won%20his%20first%20election%20in%202013%20and%20repeated%20his%20performance%20in%202018%20and%202023.%20In%20July%202020%2C%20months%20after%20the%20BJP%20snatched%20power%20from%20an%20elected%20government%20of%20the%20Congress%20through%20the%20help%20of%20rebel%20MLAs%2C%20Yadav%20took%20oath%20as%20a%20cabinet%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news%20for%20his%20controversial%20statements%20and%20for%20deploying%20invectives%20for%20his%20political%20rivals.%20In%20November%2C%20while%20campaigning%20for%20the%20election%2C%20he%20targeted%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20for%20being%20an%20%E2%80%98outsider%E2%80%99%20and%20threatened%20to%20send%20him%20packing%20to%20%E2%80%98where%20he%20came%20from%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CWill%20you%20obstruct%20the%20development%20work%20in%20Ujjain%3F%20Has%20your%20father%20fed%20you%20milk%3F%20Is%20this%20your%20status%2C%20that%20you%20will%20shut%20down%20the%20mike%20in%20the%20temple%20of%20Baba%20Mahakal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20reprimanded%20him%20and%20barred%20him%20from%20campaigning%20for%20a%20day%20for%20using%20%E2%80%9Cintemperate%20language%20transgressing%20the%20limits%20of%20decency%E2%80%9D%20in%20bypoll%20elections.%20In%20January%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Congress%20again%20complained%20to%20the%20EC%20about%20an%20alleged%20violation%20of%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20by%20Yadav%20when%20he%20posted%20a%20photograph%20of%20him%20pulling%20out%20a%20currency%20note%20from%20his%20wallet%20while%20a%20woman%20was%20applying%20tilak%20on%20his%20forehead%20during%20campaigning%20for%20the%20state%20civic%20body%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20BJP%20picked%20Yadav%20as%20its%20CM%20for%20MP%2C%20the%20Congress%20also%20started%20tweeting%20an%20old%20video%20of%20him%20making%20%E2%80%98controversial%E2%80%99%20statements%20about%20Sita.%20Speaking%20at%20an%20event%20to%20honour%20Karsevaks%20in%20December%202022%2C%20Yadav%2C%20while%20referring%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Csacrifice%E2%80%9D%20made%20by%20them%20towards%20a%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20mentioned%20the%20struggles%20of%20Sita%20in%20the%20Hindu%20epic%20Ramayan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20said%20that%20Sita%2C%20despite%20being%20pregnant%20and%20forced%20to%20give%20birth%20in%20the%20forest%2C%20continued%20to%20hold%20her%20husband%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20high%20regard%20as%20he%20had%20abandoned%20her%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20principles.%20Referring%20to%20the%20abandonment%20of%20Sita%2C%20Yadav%20equated%20it%20to%20the%20modern-day%20idea%20of%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsider%20it%20a%20life%20after%20talaq%E2%80%A6when%20someone%20is%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%20In%20the%20same%20speech%2C%20he%20also%20made%20remarks%2C%20which%20were%20interpreted%20by%20some%20as%20him%20suggesting%20that%20Sita%20committed%20suicide%20in%20front%20of%20her%20husband.%20Although%20Yadav%20later%20clarified%20his%20comments%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20only%20defining%20the%20sacrifice%20and%20devotion%20needed%20to%20build%20a%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20the%20Congress%20accused%20him%20of%20insulting%20Sita%20and%20even%20raised%20it%20in%20the%20state%20Assembly.%20On%20Monday%2C%20while%20sharing%20a%20clip%20of%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20media%20advisor%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%20Piyush%20Babele%20tweeted%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20is%20giving%20MP%20such%20a%20CM%20who%20had%20insulted%20Mata%20Sita%20from%20a%20public%20platform.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20deputy%20CMs%2C%20Devda%20and%20Shukla%2C%20also%20held%20ministerial%20portfolios%20in%20the%20last%20government.%20Devda%2C%20who%20won%20six%20elections%20before%20this%20and%20has%20been%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20previous%20Chouhan%20governments%2C%20held%20the%20finance%20and%20commercial%20tax%20department.%20Devda%20started%20his%20career%20with%20student%20union%20politics%20and%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20winning%20his%20first%20election%20in%201990.%20He%20is%20currently%20an%20MLA%20from%20Malhargarh%20constituency%20in%20Mandsaur%2C%20which%20falls%20in%20the%20northern%20belt%20of%20Malwa%20region%20of%20the%20state%2C%20close%20to%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20won%20his%20fifth%20consecutive%20election%20from%20Rewa%2C%20which%20is%20located%20on%20the%20eastern%20fringes%20of%20the%20state%20in%20the%20Vindhya%20region.%20He%20was%20inducted%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20in%20its%20last%20cabinet%20reshuffle%20in%20August%2C%202023%2C%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20163%20out%20of%20the%20230%20seats%20with%20its%20highest-ever%20vote%20percentage%20of%2048.55%25%20while%20the%20Congress%20tally%20fell%20to%2066%20seats%20even%20though%20it%20retained%20its%20vote%20share%20of%2040.40%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChouhan%2C%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20described%20Yadav%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Chardworking%20colleague.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20full%20faith%20that%20under%20the%20able%20guidance%20of%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20you%20will%20take%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20new%20heights%20of%20progress%20and%20development%20and%20will%20create%20new%20records%20in%20public%20welfare%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chouhan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%2C%20in%20his%20thanksgiving%20speech%2C%20referred%20to%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20party%20worker.%E2%80%9D%20Born%20in%201965%2C%20Yadav%20is%20also%20the%20state%20president%20of%20the%20MP%20Wrestling%20Association%20and%20state%20vice-president%20of%20the%20MP%20Olympic%20Federation.%C2%A0%20He%20holds%20a%20doctorate%20degree%20and%20as%20per%20his%20official%20profile%20in%20the%20state%20Assembly%2C%20states%20lawyer%2C%20business%20and%20farming%20as%20his%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20new%20government%20led%20by%20a%20fresh%20face%20under%2060%20years%20old%20also%20increases%20the%20generation%20gap%20between%20the%20party%20and%20its%20rival%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20still%20led%20by%20two%20veterans%20Kamal%20Nath%20and%20Digvijaya%20Singh%2C%20aged%2077%20and%2076.%C2%A0%20How%20the%20Congress%20tries%20to%20counter%20Yadav%2C%20who%20also%20brings%20in%20a%20sharper%20rhetoric%20on%20Hindutva%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20passive%20Chouhan%2C%20emerges%20as%20a%20new%20challenge%20for%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20as%20it%20not%20only%20tries%20to%20recover%20ground%20in%20the%20upcoming%20general%20election%20but%20also%20develop%20a%20leadership%20for%20the%20next%20state%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20such%20a%20large%20mandate%2C%20it%20appears%20it%20could%20also%20be%20facing%20a%20problem%20of%20plenty%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20power%20sharing%20and%20satisfying%20various%20factions%2C%20including%20one%20led%20by%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia.%20However%2C%20given%20its%20comfortable%20position%20it%20can%20afford%20to%20experiment%20and%20get%20a%20few%20things%20wrong%20as%20it%20conducts%C2%A0a%20change%20in%20leadership%20after%20two%20decades.%20For%20a%20start%2C%20by%20picking%20a%20Yadav%2C%20a%20community%20it%20tries%20to%20demonize%20in%20states%20such%20as%20Bihar%20and%20UP%2C%20to%20polarize%20other%20OBCs%2C%20the%20party%20may%20also%20be%20widening%20its%20umbrella%20of%20support%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Opposition%2C%20left%20with%20no%20choice%2C%20has%20resorted%20to%20pursuing%20backward%20caste%20politics%2C%20albeit%20nascent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20next%20for%20Chouhan%2C%20is%20also%20a%20question%20that%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20discussed%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%20Soon%20after%20the%20results%20were%20declared%20on%20December%203%2C%20Chouhan%2C%20emerging%20from%20the%20sidelines%20to%20reclaim%20his%20importance%20in%20the%20state%20politics%2C%20got%20into%20campaign%20mode%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20with%20his%20Mission%2029%E2%80%94a%20target%20to%20win%20all%20the%20LS%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20held%20public%20meetings%20in%20districts%20where%20the%20BJP%20lost%20and%20ensured%20the%20voters%20were%20reminded%20of%20the%20role%20of%20his%20flagship%20schemes%2C%20especially%20those%20for%20women%2C%20behind%20the%20huge%20mandate.%20Addressing%20workers%20in%20Raghogarh%2C%20however%2C%20he%20did%20drop%20hints%20that%20he%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20the%20CM.%20%E2%80%9CMama%20aur%20bhaiya%20padh%20duniya%20mein%20kisi%20ki%20padh%20se%20bada%20hain.%20(The%20status%20of%20a%20maternal%20uncle%20and%20brother%20is%20higher%20than%20any%20other%20post%20in%20the%20world)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20Mohan%20Yadav%20be%20able%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20mama%20of%20MP%20politics%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702314767000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11223229%2FEffect-25.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-bjp-names-mohan-yadav-an-obc-leader-with-rss-roots-as-the-next-cm%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20dilly-dallying%20for%20a%20week%2C%20the%20BJP%20legislature%20party%20finally%20elected%20Yadav%20(58)%2C%20a%20three-time%20MLA%20who%20held%20the%20higher%20education%20department%20as%20a%20minister%20under%20the%20outgoing%20BJP%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-bjp-names-mohan-yadav-an-obc-leader-with-rss-roots-as-the-next-cm%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22S