itional-charge-123121101220_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JNU%20Bans%20Protests%20On%20Campus%3B%20Attempt%20To%20Stamp%20Out%20Dissent%2C%20Say%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPutting%20up%20wall%20posters%20and%20staging%20dharnas%20within%20100%20metres%20of%20the%20academic%20buildings%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%20or%20expulsion%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20manual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20academic%20buildings%20of%20different%20schools%20house%20offices%20of%20chairpersons%2C%20deans%2C%20and%20other%20important%20office-bearers%2C%20apart%20from%20classrooms%20and%20labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20protests%20within%20100%20metres%20of%20the%20administrative%20blocks%2C%20which%20house%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%2C%20registrar%2C%20and%20proctors%2C%20among%20others%2C%20was%20prohibited%20as%20per%20a%20High%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20the%20revised%20Chief%20Proctor%20Office%20(CPO)%20manual%2C%20the%20university%20has%20now%20barred%20protests%20within%20100%20metres%20of%20academic%20buildings%20as%20well%20where%20classes%20are%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20comes%20after%20the%20JNU%20in%20October%20witnessed%20an%20incident%20where%20an%20%26quot%3Banti-national%26quot%3B%20slogan%20was%20scribbled%20on%20the%20School%20of%20Languages%20building%20wall%20and%20the%20administration%20announced%20to%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20repeated%20nature%20of%20such%20incidents%20on%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JNU%20Students'%20Union%20(JNUSU)%20has%20opposed%20the%20new%20rules%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20stifle%20dissent%20on%20campus%20and%20demanded%20its%20withdrawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stringent%20measures%20outlined%20in%20the%20manual%20are%20aimed%20at%20stifling%20the%20vibrant%20campus%20culture%20that%20has%20defined%20JNU%20for%20decades.%20The%20JNUSU%20demands%20that%20the%20university%20administration%20immediately%20revoke%20the%20new%20manual%20of%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Proctor%20Manual%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20students'%20union%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalls%20and%20texts%20to%20JNU%20registrar%20Ravikesh%20did%20not%20elicit%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20approved%20by%20the%20Executive%20Council%20in%20a%20meeting%20on%20November%2024%2C%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%20Santishree%20Dhulipudi%20Pandit%20or%20the%20competent%20authority%20will%20have%20the%20power%20to%20deem%20an%20act%20punishable%20if%20they%20find%20it%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20disciple%20and%20conduct%20in%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20have%20the%20power%20to%20waive%2C%20change%20or%20uphold%20the%20punishment%20if%20deemed%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20has%20prohibited%20printing%2C%20circulating%20or%20pasting%20posters%20or%20pamphlets%20carrying%20any%20kind%20of%20derogatory%20religious%2C%20communal%2C%20casteist%20or%20anti-national%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20act%20to%20incite%20intolerance%20towards%20a%20religion%2C%20caste%2C%20or%20community%20or%20an%20activity%20which%20is%20deemed%20%26quot%3Banti-national%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20imposed%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20student%20is%20found%20involved%20in%20a%20hunger%20strike%2C%20dharna%2C%20'group%20bargaining'%20and%20any%20other%20form%20of%20protest%20within%20100-metre%20radius%20of%20any%20academic%20and%20administrative%20complex%20or%20is%20found%20blocking%20entrance%20or%20exit%20of%20any%20of%20these%20complexes%2C%20he%20or%20she%20will%20be%20either%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%2C%20evicted%20from%20hostel%20for%20two%20months%20or%20be%20rusticated%20and%20declared%20out%20of%20bounds%20for%20up%20to%20two%20months%2C%20the%20CPO%20manual%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20forms%20of%20coercion%20such%20as%20gheraos%2C%20sit-ins%20or%20any%20variation%20of%20the%20same%20which%20disrupt%20the%20normal%20academic%20and%20administrative%20functioning%20of%20the%20university%20or%20any%20act%20inciting%20violence%20will%20be%20punished%20as%20well%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%20who%20has%20received%20five%20or%20more%20punishments%20during%20the%20duration%20of%20their%20study%20shall%20be%20expelled%20from%20the%20university%2C%20the%20manual%20noted.%20In%20case%20a%20student%20is%20found%20guilty%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20any%20of%20the%20prohibited%20activities%20and%20is%20given%20a%20punishment%2C%20he%20or%20she%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20register%20for%20the%20semester%20and%20they%20would%20not%20be%20given%20a%20'no-dues'%20certificate%20until%20the%20imposed%20fine%20is%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20will%20also%20send%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20punishment%20to%20the%20parents%20or%20guardian%20of%20the%20student%20besides%20uploading%20it%20on%20the%20official%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20student%20fails%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20proctorial%20enquiry%2C%20the%20committee%20will%20assume%20that%20the%20complaint%20was%20filed%20with%20a%20malafide%20intention%20and%20the%20student%20may%20be%20asked%20to%20perform%20community%20service%20in%20JNU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20false%20allegation%20against%20any%20student%20by%20the%20complainant%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20rustication%20from%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20university%20now%20will%20not%20allow%20cross-examination%20between%20defendant%20and%20complainant%20or%20the%20witness%2C%20which%20use%20to%20be%20an%20important%20rule%20of%20the%20proctorial%20enquiry%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vice-Chancellor's%20decision%20will%20be%20the%20final%20call%2C%20in%20case%20any%20dispute%20arises%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20interpretation%20of%20any%20of%20these%20rules%2C%20the%20manual%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702310940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-03%2Fi8cc1k9o_jawaharlal-nehru-university-jnu_625x300_29_March_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjnu-bans-protests-on-campus-attempt-to-stamp-out-dissent-says-students-4654325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Putting%20up%20wall%20posters%20and%20staging%20dharnas%20within%20100%20metres%20of%20the%20academic%20buildings%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%20or%20expulsion%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20manual.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjnu-bans-protests-on-campus-attempt-to-stamp-out-dissent-says-students-4654325%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjnu-bans-protests-on-campus-attempt-to-stamp-out-dissent-says-students-4654325%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjnu-bans-protests-on-campus-attempt-to-stamp-out-dissent-says-students-4654325%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JR%20NTR%20to%20shoot%20for%20WAR%202%20from%20March%20'24%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702310497000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105911201%2Cimgsize-36974.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjr-ntr-to-join-hrithik-roshan-for-war-2-shoot-from-march-2024-after-he-wraps-up-devara-report%2Farticleshow%2F105911207.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime