-67667172%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67667172.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67667172.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Shrugs%20Off%20Article%20370%20Ruling%20But%20May%20See%20Opportunity%20to%20Normalise%20Ties%20in%20Statehood%20Nod%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F18215053%2Findia-pakistan-flag.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Pakistan%20on%20Monday%20(December%2011)%20swiftly%20shrugged%20off%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20validating%20the%20%E2%80%98reading%20down%E2%80%99%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20amidst%20the%20continuing%20diplomatic%20tension%2C%20a%20glimmer%20of%20possibility%20emerges.%20Some%20informed%20observers%20suggest%20that%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20nod%20to%20the%20restoration%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20statehood%20could%20be%20the%20strategic%20opening%20Pakistan%20needs%20to%20extend%20an%20olive%20branch%20to%20India%20for%20talks%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-kashmir-article-370-verdict%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20affirmed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20August%202019%20decision%20to%20abolish%20the%20special%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20under%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dilution%20of%20Article%20370%E2%80%99s%20status%20had%20triggered%20Pakistan%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Farticle-370-kashmir-pakistan-downgrade-diplomatic-ties-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edowngrade%20diplomatic%20ties%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20cease%20all%20trade%20with%20India%20and%20suspend%20cross-border%20transport%20services.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20was%20not%20surprising%20that%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20immediate%20response%20was%20to%20dismiss%20the%20judgement%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EInternational%20law%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20recognize%20India%E2%80%99s%20unilateral%20and%20illegal%20actions%20of%205%20August%202019.%20The%20judicial%20endorsement%20by%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20no%20legal%20value.%20Kashmiris%20have%20an%20inalienable%20right%20to%20self%20determination%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20relevant%20UN%20SC%20resolutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jalil%20Abbas%20Jilani%20(%40JalilJilani)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJalilJilani%2Fstatus%2F1734151560903471491%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20judgement%20is%20yet%20another%20manifestation%20of%20the%20pliant%20judiciary%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20dispensation%2C%E2%80%9D%20caretaker%20foreign%20minister%20Jalil%20Abbas%20Jilani%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1796946%2Findias-top-court-upholds-end-of-special-status-for-held-kashmir-orders-polls%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Islamabad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20underlined%20that%20Pakistan%20does%20not%20recognise%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20over%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20reiterating%20its%20international%20status%20as%20a%20disputed%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPakistan%20categorically%20rejects%20the%20judgement%20announced%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20on%20the%20status%20of%20Indian%20Illegally%20Occupied%20Jammu%20Kashmir.%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20an%20internationally%20recognised%20dispute%20which%20remains%20on%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20for%20over%20seven%20decades%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20right%20to%20make%20%E2%80%9Cunilateral%20decisions%E2%80%9D%2C%20Jilani%2C%20a%20former%20Pakistani%20acting%20high%20commissioner%20to%20India%2C%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20final%20disposition%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20to%20be%20made%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20relevant%20UNSC%20and%20it%20is%20to%20be%20made%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20aspiration%20with%20the%20Kashmiri%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20said%20that%20the%20statehood%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20should%20be%20reinstated%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20unlike%20the%20deadline%20of%20September%2030%2C%202024%20to%20conduct%20elections%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20no%20clear%20timeline%20was%20provided%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20its%20statehood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20strong%20dismissal%20by%20Pakistan%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%2C%20two%20former%20Indian%20high%20commissioners%20to%20Pakistan%20believed%20that%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20as%20per%20the%20top%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20could%20provide%20space%20for%20Islamabad%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20India%20after%20elections%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20elections%20in%C2%A0both%20countries%20in%202024%2C%20it%20might%20give%20Pakistan%20a%20reason%20to%20come%20to%20the%20discussion%20table.%20But%20for%20the%20moment%20Pakistan%20will%20reject%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20India%E2%80%99s%20former%20envoy%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20Ajay%20Bisaria.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Four%20Important%20Takeaways%20From%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Ruling%20on%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffour-important-takeaways-from-the-supreme-court-ruling-on-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%3EFour%20Important%20Takeaways%20From%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Ruling%20on%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20the%20last%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20posted%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20as%20Pakistan%20downgraded%20ties%20to%20the%20deputy%20high%20commissioner-level%20in%20August%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELess%20than%20a%20year%20after%20India%20revoked%20Article%20370%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20200911050207%2Fhttps%3A%2Fthewire.in%2Fexternal-affairs%2Findia-pakistan-diplomatic-strength-cut-down%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20staff%20strength%20in%20the%20high%20commissions%20was%20halved%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20India%20chose%20to%20recall%20numerous%20officials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20decision%20came%20in%20response%20to%20Pakistan%20detaining%20two%20Indian%20diplomatic%20officials%20following%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20expulsion%20of%20Pakistani%20diplomats%20over%20alleged%20%E2%80%98espionage%E2%80%99%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESharat%20Sabharwal%2C%20who%20had%20been%20India%E2%80%99s%20high%20commissioner%20to%20Islamabad%20from%202009%20to%202013%2C%20also%20concurred%20that%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20as%20mentioned%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20in%20its%20judgement%2C%20could%20create%20an%20opportunity%20for%20Islamabad%20to%20normalise%20relations%20with%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20are%20through%20with%20their%20elections%2C%20then%20it%20could%20offer%20them%20a%20face-saving%20way%20out%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20corner%20in%20which%20they%20had%20got%20themselves%20into%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20unless%20there%20was%20a%20change%20geopolitically%20and%20the%20United%20States%20returned%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbig%20way%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20economy%20would%20remain%20in%20the%20doldrums%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20rising%20interest%20to%20improve%20ties%20with%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20my%20assessment%20that%20they%20would%20like%20to%20come%20out%20of%20that%20situation%20and%20stabilise%20things%20a%20little%20more%20with%20India.%20They%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20do%20so%20because%2C%20politically%2C%20everyone%20has%20been%20scared%20due%20to%20polarisation%20and%20other%20factors%2C%20ahead%20of%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sabharwal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-former-pm-nawaz-sharif-returns-home-from-exile%5C%22%3Ewho%20recently%20returned%20from%20exile%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20widely%20seen%20to%20be%20back%20in%20the%20good%20books%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20military%2C%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20the%20favourite%20to%20win%20the%20elections%20in%20February%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20Pakistani%20military%20will%20back%20any%20move%20by%20Sharif%20to%20restore%20trade%20ties.%20During%20his%20last%20term%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20give%20most-favoured%20nation%20status%20to%20India%20as%20per%20WTO%20rules%20was%20stymied%20by%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fnawaz-sharif-faces-an-uphill-battle-upon-return-to-pakistan%5C%22%3ENawaz%20Sharif%20Faces%20an%20Uphill%20Battle%20Upon%20Return%20to%20Pakistan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExpressing%20a%20slightly%20divergent%20perspective%2C%20Shreyas%20Deshmukh%2C%20a%20research%20associate%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Policy%20Group%2C%20contended%20that%20the%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20would%20have%20no%20impact%20on%20India-Pakistan%20relations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20argued%20that%20if%20the%20newly%20elected%20Pakistani%20government%20sought%20engagement%20with%20India%2C%20%E2%80%9Cboth%20parties%20could%20achieve%20this%20by%20setting%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20aside%20and%20initiating%20discussions%20on%20crucial%20matters%2C%20such%20as%20trade.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20decline%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20international%20standing%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20immediate%20geopolitical%20issues%20that%20could%20shift%20attention%20to%20the%20country.%20The%20evolving%20circumstances%20are%20compelling%20Pakistan%20to%20adapt%20due%20to%20economic%20challenges%2C%20political%20instability%20and%20a%20precarious%20security%20situation%2C%20leaving%20them%20with%20little%20room%20to%20dictate%20terms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20in%20a%20conundrum%20over%20its%20position%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20given%20that%20it%20was%20an%20article%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Pakistan%20wants%20to%20revert%20to%20Article%20370%2C%20for%20Kashmiris%20to%20get%20back%20some%20powers%2C%20it%20means%20it%20is%20accepting%20the%20fact%20that%20Kashmir%20is%20a%20part%20of%20Indian%20Union.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeshmukh%20expressed%20concern%20that%20there%20were%20chances%20of%20extremist%20elements%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20Pakistan%20exploiting%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20to%20aggravate%20the%20security%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20may%20see%20an%20uptick%20in%20infiltration%20attempts%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20side%20and%20attacks%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20or%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20cautioned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20also%20upheld%20the%20separation%20of%20Ladakh%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20its%20status%20as%20a%20Union%20territory.%20However%2C%20China%2C%20which%20had%20deemed%20the%20move%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunacceptable%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20react%20as%20of%20the%20time%20this%20article%20was%20written.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20claims%20Ladakh%20due%20to%20the%20continuing%20dispute%20over%20Aksai%20Chin.%20The%20Chinese%20had%20reacted%20by%20saying%20that%20the%202019%20reorganisation%20would%20%E2%80%9Cimpede%20China%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20year%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmodis-no-intrusion-by-china-claim-contradicts-indias-stand-raises-multiple-questions%5C%22%3EChinese%20troops%20began%20to%20intrude%20into%20eastern%20Ladakh%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20several%20points%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20first%20fatal%20clash%20at%20the%20border%20in%20forty%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Asian%20countries%20have%20yet%20to%20fully%20resolve%20the%20military%20stand-off%2C%20despite%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20talks%20over%20the%20last%20three-and-a-half%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702307554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F18215053%2Findia-pakistan-flag.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpakistan-article-370-statehood-nod-normalise-ties%22%2