thedailystar.net%2Fbusiness%2Fnews%2Fonion-prices-surge-supply-squeeze-after-indias-export-ban-extension-3489916%5C%22%3ETk%20105-125%20per%20kilogram%20a%20week%20ago%20to%20Tk%20180-190%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Imported%20onions%20also%20experienced%20a%20surge%2C%20increasing%20from%20Tk%2090-110%20to%20Tk%20160-170.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20than%20the%20export%20ban%2C%20retailers%20and%20wholesalers%20attributed%20the%20price%20surge%20to%20a%20crunch%20in%20domestic%20supply%20due%20to%20Cyclone%20Michaung%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Star%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Fbusiness%2Fnews%2Fonion-prices-surge-supply-squeeze-after-indias-export-ban-extension-3489916%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20market%20observers%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20restrictions%20on%20Indian%20onion%E2%80%99s%20import%20have%20been%20in%20place%20since%20October%20while%20questioning%20the%20abrupt%20surge%20and%20the%20rationale%20behind%20the%20nearly%20doubled%20prices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBhutan%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnion%20prices%20in%20Bhutan%20also%20followed%20a%20similar%20pattern%20with%20prices%20reaching%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbs.bt%2Fnews%2F%3Fp%3D195656%5C%22%3Ehigh%20as%20Nu%20150%20per%20kilogram%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20India%E2%80%99s%20ban%20on%20onion%20exports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResidents%20in%20Thimphu%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20capital%2C%20said%20that%20the%20vegetable%20was%20being%20sold%20in%20the%20range%20of%20Nu%2050-70%20per%20kilogram%20earlier.%20Similar%20price%20hikes%20were%20reported%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20Bhutan%20with%20the%20price%20rising%20from%20Nu%2070-80%20per%20kilogram%20to%20Nu%20100%20after%20India%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20a%20Bhutan%20Broadcasting%20Service%20(BBS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbs.bt%2Fnews%2F%3Fp%3D195656%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20officials%20also%20reportedly%20seized%20onions%20from%20eight%20trucks%20on%20route%20to%20Bhutan%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20vegetable%20vendors%20said%20the%20Indian%20customs%20officials%20at%20the%20border%20in%20Phuentshogling%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20them%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20onions%20they%20had%20already%20paid%20for%2C%20unaware%20of%20the%20notice%20on%20the%20ban%2C%20BBS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbs.bt%2Fnews%2F%3Fp%3D195656%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20know%20anything%20about%20the%20notice%20on%20ban%20of%20export%20when%20we%20loaded%20the%20onions.%20We%20only%20knew%20about%20it%20when%20we%20reached%20Phuentsholing%20from%20Falakata%20and%20were%20stopped%20by%20the%20custom%20office.%20We%20were%20refused%20when%20we%20requested%20them%20to%20allow%20us%20to%20take%20the%20already%20loaded%20onions%20for%20which%20we%20already%20paid.%20We%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20paid%20for%20or%20bought%20the%20onions%20had%20we%20known%20about%20the%20notice.%20The%20Indian%20officials%20refused%20even%20when%20our%20customs%20official%20tried%20to%20request%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbs.bt%2Fnews%2F%3Fp%3D195656%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tshomo%2C%20a%20vegetable%20vendor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20loaded%20the%20onions%20from%20India%20the%20day%20before%20yesterday%2C%20there%20was%20no%20notice%20on%20the%20ban.%20So%20when%20we%20reached%20the%20Indian%20customs%20office%2C%20we%20were%20stopped%20since%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20ban%20had%20been%20issued.%20We%20had%20to%20take%20out%20the%20onions%20and%20bear%20the%20loss.%20We%20would%20be%20grateful%20if%20our%20government%20%5Bcould%5D%20do%20something%20regarding%20the%20issue%20since%20we%20do%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbs.bt%2Fnews%2F%3Fp%3D195656%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Phuntsho%20Wangdi%2C%20another%20vegetable%20vendor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENepal%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENepal%20that%20relies%20almost%20entirely%20on%20India%20for%20its%20onion%20imports%20is%20also%20facing%20inflationary%20pressure%20in%20wake%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20ban.%20In%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fmoney%2F2023%2F12%2F11%2Fonions-tear-inducingly-pricey-after-india-s-ban%5C%22%3ENepal%20imported%20around%20190%20tonnes%20of%20onions%3C%2Fa%3E%20worth%20Rs%206.75%20billion%20from%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnion%20prices%20in%20the%20country%20have%20surged%2C%20nearly%20doubling%20to%20Rs%20200%20per%20kilogram%20in%20retail%2C%20following%20India%E2%80%99s%20recent%20export%20restrictions.%20Traders%20anticipate%20further%20increases%20as%20Nepal%20heavily%20relies%20on%20imported%20onions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%202019%2C%20the%20price%20of%20onion%20hit%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%20Rs%20250%20per%20kg%20in%20Kathmandu%20after%20India%20banned%20onion%20exports%20in%20September%20that%20year.%20Many%20are%20now%20concerned%20about%20onion%20prices%20crossing%20this%20benchmark%20after%20India%E2%80%99s%20latest%20announcement%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EKathmandu%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fmoney%2F2023%2F12%2F11%2Fonions-tear-inducingly-pricey-after-india-s-ban%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMaldives%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaldivian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Favas.mv%2Fen%2F137695%5C%22%3Eeconomic%20minister%20Mohamed%20Saeed%20reassured%20the%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20country%20isn%E2%80%99t%20facing%20a%20disruption%20in%20the%20import%20of%20essential%20commodities%20in%20wake%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20export%20cubs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20Nepal%2C%20Maldives%20too%20is%20reliant%20on%20onion%20exports%20from%20India.%20Onion%20prices%20in%20the%20country%20have%20increased%20owing%20to%20a%20shortage%20in%20the%20local%20market%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPreviously%20priced%20between%20MVR%20200-MVR%20350%20per%20sack%2C%20onions%20are%20now%20being%20sold%20for%20MVR%20500%20in%20some%20places%20while%20MVR%20800-MVR%20900%20in%20others%2C%20%3Cem%3EAvas%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Favas.mv%2Fen%2F137695%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20India%20has%20made%20exemptions%20for%20some%20neighbouring%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20Maldives%2C%20the%20current%20onion%20stocks%20in%20the%20Maldivian%20market%20are%20sourced%20from%20Pakistan%20and%20China%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESri%20Lanka%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20price%20of%20onions%20has%20increased%20to%20nearly%20Rs%20300%2Fkilo%20in%20the%20local%20retail%20market%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Mirror%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymirror.lk%2Fprint%2Ffront-page%2FIndias-onion-export-ban-extension-leaves-SL-importers-in-a-dilemma%2F238-272902%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20Essential%20Food%20Commodities%20Importers%20and%20Traders%20Association%20told%20the%20Daily%20Mirror%20that%20importers%20were%20exploring%20alternative%20suppliers.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20perishable%20item.%20So%2C%20we%20place%20orders%20for%20weekly%20shipments.%20It%20is%20challenging%20for%20us%20to%20look%20to%20different%20markets%20because%20prices%20are%20very%20expensive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702303030000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http