ed%20%E2%80%93%20or%20wrongly%20accused.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20person%20who%20has%20doubts%20is%20the%20judge.%20The%20judgment%20is%20less%20a%20reflection%20on%20the%20truth%20of%20the%20accusations%2C%20but%20more%20a%20reflection%20on%20the%20sagacity%20and%20logic%20of%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fpdf%2FLU%2Farticle_370.pdf%5C%22%3Ejudgment%20on%20the%20Article%20370%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20honourable%20justices%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20have%20shown%20they%20have%20nothing%20of%20sagacity%20or%20logic%3B%20but%20of%20cowardice%2C%20they%20have%20aplenty%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20many%20parts%20to%20the%20judgment%2C%20and%20it%20is%20worth%20reading%20in%20full%20because%20it%20blends%20many%20questions%20of%20law.%20Nonetheless%2C%20there%20is%20one%20issue%20that%20stands%20out%20as%20the%20heart%20and%20substance%20of%20the%20case%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20key%20differentiator%20between%20a%20democracy%20and%20a%20dictatorship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20bending%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20regime%20reinterpreted%20Article%20367%20to%20say%20that%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20legislative%20assembly%20should%20be%20regarded%20as%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Constituent%20Assembly%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20dissolved%20in%201957%20%E2%80%93%20and%20furthermore%2C%20since%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20was%20dissolved%2C%20then%20the%20governor%20was%20the%20representative%20of%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20as%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlease%20regard%20this%20carefully.%20The%20president%2C%20an%20appointee%20of%20the%20governing%20party%2C%20and%20the%20governor%2C%20another%20appointee%20of%20the%20governing%20party%2C%20are%20supposed%20to%20represent%20the%20governed.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20government%20chooses%20who%20represents%20the%20people%2C%20not%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20the%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20does%20not%20just%20go%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-chandrachud-basic-structure-north-star%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cbasic%20structure%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20constitution%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20defended%20so%20strenuously%2C%20it%20goes%20against%20democracy%20itself.%20It%20is%20only%20in%20a%20dictatorship%20that%20the%20regime%20chooses%20who%20represents%20the%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffour-important-takeaways-from-the-supreme-court-ruling-on-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%3EFour%20Important%20Takeaways%20From%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Ruling%20on%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20captured%20best%20by%20Bertolt%20Brecht%20when%20he%20wrote%20his%20satirical%20poem%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fallpoetry.com%2FThe-Solution%5C%22%3EThe%20Solution%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%2C%20in%201953%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20uprising%20of%20the%2017th%20of%20June%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Writers%E2%80%99%20Union%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHad%20leaflets%20distributed%20on%20the%20Stalinallee%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhich%20stated%20that%20the%20people%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHad%20lost%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20government%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20could%20only%20win%20it%20back%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20redoubled%20work.%20Would%20it%20not%2C%20in%20that%20case%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBe%20simpler%20for%20the%20government%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20dissolve%20the%20people%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20elect%20another%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20Indian%20government%20is%20open%20to%20ideas%20and%20blind%20to%20satire%2C%20it%20has%20done%20just%20that%3A%C2%A0arguing%20that%20it%20had%20dissolved%20the%20people%20and%20elected%20another%2C%20since%20%E2%80%93%20after%20all%20%E2%80%93%20if%20its%20appointees%20were%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20people%2C%20it%20could%20change%20them%20at%20will.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20its%20infinite%20wisdom%20which%20has%20been%20on%20display%20in%20a%20slew%20of%20cases%20whether%20involving%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20non-hearing%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20habeas%20corpus%20petitions%20that%20were%20allowed%20to%20languish%20for%20a%20year%20and%20its%20sublime%20indifference%20to%20the%20evisceration%20of%20its%20%3Cem%3EPuttaswamy%3C%2Fem%3E%20judgment%2C%20has%20now%20put%20its%20imprimatur%20on%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20this%20makes%20sense%2C%20well%2C%20that%20is%20not%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20business.%20I%20mean%2C%20if%20it%20could%20maintain%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fbabri-masjid%2F%5C%22%3EBabri%20Masjid%20demolition%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20demolition%20was%20wrong%20but%20those%20who%20committed%20the%20crime%20should%20retain%20custody%20of%20what%20they%20had%20grasped%20through%20the%20crime%2C%20well%20then%2C%20anything%20is%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20regarding%20Kashmir%2C%20where%20all%20our%20pieties%20about%20democracy%2C%20liberalism%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20have%20gone%20to%20die%2C%20burying%20rationality%20in%20an%20unmarked%20grave%20along%20with%20so%20many%20others%20will%20be%20nothing%20new.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp