0px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20total%20of%2065.9%25%20of%20houses%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana-Urban%20(PMAY-U)%20have%20been%20completed%20and%20delivered%20to%20beneficiaries%20since%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20inception%20in%202015%20until%20December%204.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20flagship%20scheme%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20seeks%20to%20provide%20housing%20for%20all%20to%20the%20urban%20poor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Monday%2C%20minister%20of%20state%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Affairs%20Kaushal%20Kishore%20said%20that%20PMAY-U%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdemand-driven%20scheme%20and%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20fixed%20any%20target%20for%20construction%20of%20houses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%20has%20been%20implemented%20under%20the%20%E2%80%9CHousing%20for%20All%E2%80%9D%20Mission%20since%20June%202015%20to%20provide%20Central%20assistance%20to%20implementing%20agencies%20through%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20(UTs)%20for%20providing%20all-weather%20pucca%20houses%20with%20basic%20civic%20services%20to%20all%20eligible%20urban%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20figures%20given%20by%20Kishore%20in%20his%20reply%201%2C18%2C63%2C073%20have%20been%20sanctioned%2C%201%2C13%2C42%2C815%20have%20been%20grounded%20and%2078%2C26%2C765%20have%20been%20completed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPMAY-U%20is%20a%20demand%20driven%20scheme%20and%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20fixed%20any%20target%20for%20construction%20of%20houses.%20Based%20on%20the%20project%20proposals%20submitted%20by%20States%2F%20UTs%2C%20as%20on%2004.12.2023%2C%20118.63%20lakh%20houses%20have%20been%20sanctioned%20under%20PMAY-U%2C%20out%20of%20which%20113.43%20lakh%20have%20been%20grounded%20for%20construction%3B%20of%20which%2078.27%20lakh%20have%20been%20completed%2F%20delivered%20to%20beneficiaries%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kishore%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKishore%20said%20that%20the%20timeline%20for%20completion%20of%20projects%20varies%20from%20state%20to%20state%20and%20generally%20takes%20around%2012%20to%2036%20months.%20The%20scheme%20period%20which%20had%20earlier%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20March%202022%20has%20been%20extended%20up%20to%20December%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20provided%20figures%20for%20the%20houses%20sanctioned%20under%20the%20scheme%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202020-21%20a%20total%20of%2016%2C81%2C038%20houses%20were%20sanctioned%2C%2018%2C14%2C606%20in%202021-22%20and%2010%2C01%2C739%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20monsoon%20session%20in%20July%20this%20year%2C%20minister%20for%20housing%20and%20urban%20affairs%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20told%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20that%20a%20total%20of%2075.51%20lakh%20houses%20have%20been%20completed%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20which%2071.39%20lakh%20have%20been%20occupied%2C%20reported%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fparliament-proceedings-7551-lakh-houses-completed-under-pmay-u%2Farticle67142907.ece%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20had%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20houses%20completed%20at%2012%2C87%2C307%2C%20while%20Gujarat%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20were%20the%20other%20high-performing%20states%20with%208%2C80%2C209%20and%208%2C08%2C278%20houses%20completed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702296950000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn