y%20created%20castes%20to%20suit%20the%20kind%20of%20service%20they%20required.%20The%20system%20has%20been%20designed%20and%20concocted%20step%20by%20step.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%20castes%20currently%20referred%20to%20as%20Scheduled%20Castes%20in%20the%20constitution%20were%20required%20to%20provide%20services%20which%20have%20been%20considered%20extremely%20repulsive.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20are%20some%20caste%20groups%20in%20this%20grouping%20who%20are%20not%20involved%20in%20activities%20considered%20disgusting%2C%20and%20yet%20they%20had%20been%20categorised%20as%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99.%20One%20such%20caste%20is%20Dabgar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20438px)%2085vw%2C%20438px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22438%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22627%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDabgars%20have%20a%20minuscule%20population%20in%20Bihar.%20According%20to%20the%20Caste%20Based%20Census%20Report%202022%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20their%20number%20is%20only%207%2C756%20and%20they%20are%20ranked%20ninth%20in%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes.%20According%20to%20a%20socio%20economic%20report%20of%20caste-based%20enumeration%20presented%20by%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20the%20Bihar%20legislative%20assembly%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Dabgar%20caste%20are%20the%20richest%20among%20all%20the%2022%20castes%20included%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20families%20whose%20monthly%20income%20is%20Rs%206%2C000%20or%20less%20have%20been%20categorised%20as%20%E2%80%98poor%E2%80%99.%20On%20this%20basis%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20found%20that%20the%20poorest%20of%20the%20poor%20among%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20of%20the%20state%20are%20the%20people%20of%20Musahar%20caste%2C%20of%20whom%2C%2054.46%25%20families%20have%20a%20monthly%20income%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%206%2C000.%20Next%20are%20the%20people%20of%20Bhuiyan%20caste%2C%20who%20are%20equivalent%20to%20the%20Musahar%20caste%20at%20the%20social%20level.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%2053.55%25%20Bhuiyan%20families%20are%20poor.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20poor%20families%20of%20the%20Dabgar%20caste%20group%20is%20less%20than%20the%20percentage%20of%20poor%20families%20of%20Pasi%20caste%20(38.14%25).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20Dabgar%20is%20not%20a%20caste%20native%20to%20Bihar.%20Its%20people%20originally%20hailed%20from%20Rajasthan%20and%20made%20special%20kind%20of%20vessels%20to%20be%20used%20as%20spoons%20and%20ladles.%20They%20used%20wood%20and%20iron%20to%20make%20the%20utensils.%20Since%20spoons%20are%20pressed%20to%20give%20them%20a%20sunken%20shape%2C%20their%20makers%20were%20called%20%3Cem%3Edabgar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20of%20this%20caste%20used%20to%20make%20earthen%20stoves%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echulhas%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20houses%20of%20people%20of%20other%20castes%2C%20while%20men%20made%20flasks%2C%20ladles%20and%20other%20types%20of%20spoons.%20Due%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20their%20work%2C%20this%20caste%20group%20came%20to%20be%20regarded%20differently%20from%20other%20Scheduled%20Castes.%20However%2C%20even%20the%20necessity%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Echulha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E-making%20did%20not%20ensure%20that%20the%20women%20of%20this%20caste%20could%20enter%20the%20houses%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20castes.%20They%20made%20stoves%20outside%20their%20homes%20and%20when%20the%20stove%20was%20ready%2C%20they%20were%20handed%20grains%2C%20etc.%20as%20wages.%20Once%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Echulha%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20ready%2C%20a%20purification%20ritual%20was%20carried%20out%20after%20which%20the%20stoves%20made%20by%20the%20Dabgars%20were%20taken%20inside%20the%20house%20and%20placed%20in%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Dabgar%20caste%20are%20engaged%20in%20making%20neither%20spoons%20nor%20stoves%2C%20except%20during%20the%20Chhath%20festival.%20Because%20they%20made%20funnels%2C%20they%20also%20came%20in%20touch%20with%20people%20of%20the%20Teli%20caste.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20Dabgar%20caste%20eventually%20took%20to%20farming%20and%20other%20occupations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20progress%20of%20any%20caste%20depends%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20its%20relationship%20with%20prosperous%20castes.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20biggest%20reason%20behind%20the%20poor%20condition%20of%20Musahar%20families%20is%20that%20they%20have%20been%20kept%20distant%20from%20the%20affluent%20castes.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20Dom%20caste%20only%20cross%20paths%20with%20the%20people%20of%20affluent%20castes%20at%20cremation%20grounds%20or%20while%20cleaning%20dirty%20drains.%20In%20Bihar%2C%2053.10%25%20Dom%20families%20live%20on%20an%20income%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Moreover%2C%20for%20a%20caste%20whose%20total%20population%20is%20less%20than%208%2C000%2C%20individual%20affluence%20does%20not%20matter%20much.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20this%20caste%20is%20included%20among%20the%20castes%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20extinction.%20Had%20the%20cause%20of%20extinction%20been%20the%20eradication%20of%20the%20concept%20of%20caste%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20different%20matter%2C%20but%20that%20is%20not%20the%20case.%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20have%20now%20stopped%20calling%20themselves%20Dabgar%20and%20have%20merged%20themselves%20with%20other%20castes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20it%20is%20only%20due%20to%20caste%20reservation%20that%207%2C756%20people%20in%20Bihar%20still%20believe%20that%20they%20belong%20to%20the%20Dabgar%20caste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F261396%2Fbihar-caste-survey-dabgar-caste-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-wh