0existed%20in%20August%201947%20remains%20divided%20on%20the%20ceasefire%20line%2C%20and%20hence%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20bleeding%20humanitarian%20and%20political%20issue%2C%20begging%20redressal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeightened%20security%20measures%20were%20put%20in%20place%2C%20especially%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20on%20Monday.%20At%20many%20places%2C%20checkpoints%20were%20set%20up%20where%20security%20personnel%20stopped%20the%20vehicles%20and%20frisked%20the%20commuters%20before%20allowing%20them%20to%20proceed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Srinagar%20city%2C%20a%20businessman%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20(in%20Kashmir)%20had%20correctly%20guessed%20the%20decision%20even%20before%20it%20was%20delivered%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20There%20was%20no%20expectation%20of%20any%20different%20verdict%20and%20there%20is%20little%20we%20can%20do%20to%20change%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20leader%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20were%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20apex%20court%2C%20which%20has%20no%20political%20affiliation%2C%20was%20our%20last%20hope.%20Article%20370%20and%20Article%2035-A%20were%20historical%20features%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20will%20hurt%20our%20people%20and%20our%20economy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Azad%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%E2%80%99s%20Conference%20President%20Sajad%20Lone%2C%20who%20was%20also%20stopped%20from%20addressing%20the%20media%2C%20expressed%20disappointment%20with%20the%20verdict.%20Karan%20Singh%2C%20the%20grandson%20of%20Maharaja%20Hari%20Singh%20who%20was%20the%20last%20Dogra%20ruler%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20urged%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20accept%20the%20SC%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20elections%20which%20have%20been%20delayed%20for%20more%20than%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20scenes%20of%20jubilation%20were%20witnessed%20in%20parts%20of%20Jammu%2C%20where%20some%20middle-rung%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20activists%20were%20seen%20dancing%20on%20the%20roads%20and%20distributing%20sweets%20to%20celebrate%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702293346000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11163902%2Fomar-mehbooba.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsubdued-response-jk-political-parties-sc-uphold-article-370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20and%20Omar%20Abdullah%20said%20they%20were%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20rejected%20the%20claim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20May%20Join%20Kolkata%20'Gita'%20Recital%20by%20Those%20Behind%20Controversial%20Bengal%20Kumbh%20'Revival'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11152724%2FModi-with-Gita-recital-organisers-in-November.-Photo-shared-on-Facebook-by-organisers.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20expected%20to%20attend%20an%20event%20in%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20Brigade%20Parade%20Ground%20where%201%20lakh%20people%20are%20set%20to%20be%20mobilised%20to%20recite%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3EBhagvad%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EGita%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20December%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECuriously%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20its%20associated%20organisations%20belonging%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20fa