ir%20invitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20praise%20and%20a%20dubious%20history%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELast%20year%2C%20PM%20Modi%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1902487%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%253D1902487%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702361623589000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3JCMdiBy0U5PRxwYDDkgBL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epraised%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%E2%80%9Crevival%E2%80%9D%20of%20Tribeni%20Kumbh%20Mela%20in%20Hooghly%20district%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20700%20years%E2%80%9D.%20The%20fair%20allegedly%20stopped%20seven%20centuries%20ago%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20aggression.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20it%20was%20later%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fhindutva-a-tampered-research-paper-pm-s-endorsement-drive-effort-to-revive-kumbh-mela-in-trinamool-ruled-west-bengal-645daf6b521bc%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fhindutva-a-tampered-research-paper-pm-s-endorsement-drive-effort-to-revive-kumbh-mela-in-trinamool-ruled-west-bengal-645daf6b521bc%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702361623589000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2rn5lR-gXtnyLAcUJ4v5W5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20revival%20was%20a%20concocted%20story%20based%20on%20the%20doctoring%20of%20an%20Oxford%20University%20PhD%20thesis%20from%20the%201970s.%20In%20reality%2C%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20record%20of%20any%20Kumbh%20Mela%20happening%20in%20Tribeni%2C%20or%20West%20Bengal%2C%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Falan-morinis-p