E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20UPSC%20allows%20you%20to%20broaden%20your%20knowledge%20horizon.%20If%20I%20had%20been%20just%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20would%20have%20not%20read%20geography%2C%20civics%2C%20or%20economics.%20During%20preparation%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20about%20my%20country%20in%20detail.%20This%20is%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2035-year-old%2C%20who%20did%20not%20take%20medicine%20as%20her%20optional%20but%20a%20new%20subject%20%E2%80%94%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saloni%20completed%20her%20MBBS%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lady%20Hardinge%20Medical%20College%20in%202012.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334805%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaloni%20completed%20her%20MBBS%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lady%20Hardinge%20Medical%20College%20in%202012.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaloni%E2%80%99s%20quest%20for%20knowledge%20helped%20her%20crack%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321822%2Fraised-by-single-mom-ias-officer-donge-revaiah-shares-inspiring-upsc-journey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20examination%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20her%20very%20first%20attempt.%20With%20a%20year%E2%80%99s%20preparation%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20achieve%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2074.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Saloni%20was%20allocated%20to%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20cadre.%20Post%20her%20marriage%20with%20IAS%20Ashish%20Vashishta%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20cadre.%20For%20their%20marriage%2C%20Saloni%20paid%20a%20court%20fee%20of%20Rs%20500%20and%20reported%20to%20work%20within%20two%20days.%20She%20has%20been%20praised%20for%20her%20simplicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202014-batch%20IAS%20officer%20shares%20her%20strategy%20for%20the%20first-time%20aspirants%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20not%20follow%20what%20everyone%20else%20does%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20advises%20UPSC%20aspirants%20to%20not%20follow%20a%20blanket%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFigure%20out%20what%20works%20out%20best%20for%20you.%20You%20need%20to%20have%20a%20very%20customised%20approach%20for%20yourself.%20Some%20people%20prefer%20studying%20in%20groups%2C%20some%20prefer%20to%20study%20alone%20in%20a%20room.%20That%20is%20totally%20okay%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBe%20consistent%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20Saloni%20had%20roughly%20a%20year%20for%20preparation%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20be%20consistent%20in%20her%20preparation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPreparing%20for%20UPSC%20is%20not%20a%20100-metre%20race.%20It%20is%20a%20marathon.%20Here%2C%20you%20have%20to%20study%20for%20at%20least%20a%20whole%20year.%20You%20cannot%20have%20abrupt%20moments%20of%20very%20extensive%20study%20and%20then%20go%20into%20a%20shell%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20opines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-wi