2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dhanush%20Biopic%20on%20Isaignani%20Ilaiyaraaja%3A%20The%20Real%20Story%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Musical%20Sage%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIlaiyaraaja%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298846%2Fponniyin-selvan-must-watch-mani-ratnam-movies-yuva-alaipayuthey-nayakan-indian-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprolific%20musicians%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%20has%20seen.%20The%20composer%20has%20regaled%20millions%20with%20his%20tunes%20for%20over%20five%20decades.%20Fondly%20called%20Raaja%2C%20the%2080-year-old%20has%20fans%20across%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Pannaipuram%20village%20in%20Theni%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20he%20stormed%20into%20the%20music%20industry%20in%20the%2070s%2C%20and%20ruled%20the%20Tamil%20music%20industry%20for%20several%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20composed%20over%208%2C000%20songs%20in%201%2C000%20films%20and%20has%20enthralled%20audiences%20through%20his%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20conferred%20with%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%2C%20the%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20and%20five%20National%20Awards%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98Isaignani%E2%80%99%20(the%20musical%20sage)%20and%20was%20conferred%20the%20title%20%E2%80%98Maestro%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Royal%20Philharmonic%20Orchestra%2C%20London%2C%20being%20the%20first%20Asian%20composer%20to%20record%20a%20symphony%20with%20them%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20credited%20with%20changing%20the%20way%20music%20is%20made%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247945%2Fsp-balasubrahmanyam-spb-padma-vibhushan-award-2021-singer-music-world-record-roja-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Tamil%20films.%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20composers%20to%20use%20Western%20classical%20music%20and%20arrangements%20in%20his%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Tamil%20cinema%2C%20he%20has%20also%20scored%20music%20for%20Telugu%2C%20Kannada%2C%20Malayalam%20and%20Hindi%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3ECheeni%20Kum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EPaa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20humble%20background%20and%20upbringing%20heavily%20influenced%20his%20musical%20journey%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20his%20music%20infused%20with%20elements%20of%20regular%2C%20everyday%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20biopic%20on%20the%20maestro%20is%20in%20the%20making%20and%20actor%20Dhanush%20will%20reportedly%20essay%20the%20role.%20According%20to%20the%20reports%2C%20the%20film%20will%20go%20on%20floors%20in%202024%20and%20be%20released%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilm%20trade%20analyst%20Manobala%20Vijayabalan%20confirmed%20the%20news%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fan-artiste-of-the-millennium-ilaiyaraaja-at-75%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98An%20Artiste%20of%20the%20Millennium%3A%20Ilaiyaraaja%20at%2075%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Karthikeyan%20Damodaran%20for%20The%20Wire%2C%20Published%20on%2010%20September%2C%202018%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmovies%2Fregional-cinema%2Fstory%2Fdhanush-to-play-isaignani-ilaiyaraaja-in-upcoming-biopic-2456654-2023-11-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Dhanush%20to%20play%20Isaignani%20Ilaiyaraaja%20in%20upcoming%20biopic%3F%E2%